%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Biggest%20Ever%20Drug%20Bust%2C%20Over%203%2C300%20Kg%20Of%20Meth%2C%20Charas%20Seized%20In%20Gujarat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20joint%20operation%2C%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20and%20the%20Narcotics%20Control%20Bureau%20(NCB)%20on%20Tuesday%20seized%20around%203%2C300%20kg%20of%20drugs%20from%20a%20ship%20near%20Gujarat's%20Porbandar%2C%20making%20it%20the%20biggest-ever%20drug%20seizure%20in%20the%20country%2C%20the%20Navy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20a%20small%20ship%20was%20intercepted%20by%20the%20Navy%20and%20over%203089%20kg%20of%20charas%2C%20158%20kg%20of%20methamphetamine%20and%2025%20kg%20of%20morphine%20was%20recovered.%20The%20ship's%20five%20crew%2C%20all%20Pakistani%20nationals%2C%20have%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FIndianNavy%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23IndianNavy%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20coordinated%20ops%20with%20Narcotics%20Control%20Bureau%2C%20apprehended%20a%20suspicious%20dhow%20carrying%20almost%203300Kgs%20contraband%20(3089%20Kgs%20Charas%2C%20158%20Kgs%20Methamphetamine%2025%20Kgs%20Morphine).%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20largest%20seizure%20of%20narcotics%2C%20in%20quantity%20in%20recent%20times.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarcoticsbureau%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40narcoticsbureau%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FRPvzI1fdLW%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FRPvzI1fdLW%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20SpokespersonNavy%20(%40indiannavy)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Findiannavy%2Fstatus%2F1762672069865841062%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2028%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20seizure%20of%20drugs%20from%20the%20dhow%2C%20which%20is%20by%20far%20the%20largest%20in%20terms%20of%20quantity%2C%20was%20possible%20through%20the%20collaborative%20efforts%20of%20the%20Indian%20Navy's%20mission-deployed%20assets%20with%20the%20NCB.%20The%20contraband%20along%20with%20the%20apprehended%20boat%20and%20crew%20have%20been%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20Law%20Enforcement%20Agencies%20at%20an%20Indian%20port%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20Navy%20said%20a%20suspicious%20dhow%20(sailing%20vessel)%20was%20spotted%20at%20sea%20near%20Porbandar%20by%20a%20surveillance%20aircraft%20after%20which%20a%20ship%20was%20diverted%20to%20intercept%20the%20vessel%20believed%20to%20be%20engaged%20in%20drug%20smuggling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20the%20input%20of%20P8I%20LRMR%20aircraft%20on%20surveillance%20mission%2C%20IN%20mission-deployed%20ship%20was%20diverted%20to%20intercept%20the%20suspicious%20dhow%20engaged%20in%20contraband%20smuggling%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Navy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20massive%20drug%20bust%20comes%20a%20week%20after%20a%20staggering%201%2C100%20kilograms%20of%20the%20mephedrone%2C%20also%20known%20by%20its%20street%20name%20'Meow%20Meow'%2C%20worth%20Rs%202%2C500%20crore%20was%20seized%20in%20two-day%20raids%20across%20Pune%20and%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20700%20kg%20of%20mephedrone%20was%20seized%20in%20Pune%20and%20another%20400%20kg%20of%20the%20banned%20drug%20was%20found%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709091780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fg381uho_indian-navy-drugs_625x300_28_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-biggest-ever-drug-bust-over-3-300-kg-of-meth-charas-seized-in-gujarat-5141448%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20joint%20operation%2C%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20and%20the%20Narcotics%20Control%20Bureau%20(NCB)%20on%20Tuesday%20seized%20around%203%2C300%20kg%20of%20drugs%20from%20a%20ship%20near%20Gujarat's%20Porbandar%2C%20m