2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-updates-nse-bse-sensex-nifty-today-midcap-smallcap-voda-idea-patanjali-feb-28-124022800096_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rajya%20Sabha%20Elections%20Wrap%3A%20Cross-Voting%20Defines%20Polls%20in%20Three%20States%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F28090303%2FGHXEae5WYAA-d2I.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Cross%20voting%20dominated%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections%20on%20February%2027%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20dealing%20a%20shock%20upset%20to%20the%20Congress%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20but%20managing%20to%20get%20all%20its%20three%20candidates%20elected%20in%20Karnataka.%20In%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20eight%20out%20of%2010%20BJP%20candidates%20won.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Fpolitics%2Fhimachal-pradesh-ruling-congress-suffers-jolt-loses-rajya-sabha-election-to-bjp%3Futm%3Dauthorlistpage%5C%22%3EHigh%20drama%20dominated%20the%20elections%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20the%20Congress%20is%20in%20power%2C%20but%20saw%20its%20candidate%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%20losing%20to%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Harsh%20Mahajan%20by%20a%20draw%20of%20votes%20following%20a%20tie.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAddressing%20reporters%20after%20the%20elections%20were%20declared%20in%20favour%20of%20Mahajan%2C%20Singhvi%20said%20that%20the%20saffron%20party%20needs%20to%20%E2%80%9Cintrospect%20and%20think%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFirst%20of%20all%2C%20I%20extend%20heartiest%20congratulations%20to%20Harsh%20Mahajan%2C%20he%20has%20won.%20He%20deserves%20my%20congratulations.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20tell%20his%20party%20%E2%80%93%20introspect%20and%20think.%20When%20a%2025-member%20party%20fields%20a%20candidate%20against%20a%2043-member%20party%2C%20there%20is%20just%20one%20message%2C%20we%20will%20shamelessly%20do%20that%20which%20is%20not%20permitted%20by%20the%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20think%20one%20person%20or%20two%20persons%20or%20nine%20persons%20can%20come%20up%20with%20a%20new%20ideology%20after%20last%20night%E2%80%99s%20dinner%20and%20this%20morning%E2%80%99s%20breakfast%20then%20I%20believe%20we%20are%20all%20living%20in%20a%20fool%E2%80%99s%20paradise.%20This%20change%20is%20very%20unfortunate%20for%20India%20and%20especially%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20culture%20of%20its%20people%20were%20not%20part%20of%20this%20culture.%20If%20this%20is%20the%20definition%20of%20new%20India%20then%20I%20would%20prefer%20the%20older%20definition.%20Even%20while%20losing%20we%20have%20made%20history.%20Despite%20so%20many%20changes%20of%20heart%2C%20they%20could%20not%20change%20one%20more%20heart%20and%20it%20was%20tied%20at%2034.%20Perhaps%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20a%20tie%20has%20happened%20despite%20such%20efforts%20by%20our%20friends.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EVIDEO%20%7C%20Here%E2%80%99s%20what%20BJP%20leader%20Harsh%20Mahajan%20said%20after%20winning%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seat%20from%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20credit%20for%20my%20victory%20goes%20to%20my%20party%20(BJP)%20for%20nominating%20me%20as%20the%20candidate.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20thank%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20state%20and%20central%20leadership%20for%20their%20support%20and%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FRFbcMuUElg%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FRFbcMuUElg%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20(%40PTI_News)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPTI_News%2Fstatus%2F1762522298525810994%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2027%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seat%20was%20up%20for%20grabs%20from%20the%20state%20in%20which%20the%2068-member%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20Assembly%20has%2040%20Congress%2040%20MLAs%20at%20present%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20has%2025%20and%20three%20are%20independents.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20votes%20being%20tied%20at%2034%2C%20it%20became%20clear%20that%20nine%20members%20of%20the%20Congress%20had%20cross%20voted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20also%20like%20to%20thank%20the%20nine%20persons%20because%20they%20have%20taught%20me%20a%20lot%20about%20human%20nature%2C%20its%20fickleness%20or%20its%20resoluteness%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Singhvi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20supped%20with%20us%20(in%20Biblical%20terms)%20because%20they%20had%20dinner%20with%20us%20and%20few%20of%20them%20had%20breakfast%20with%20us.%20So%2C%20I%20think%20we%20are%20bad%20judges%20of%20human%20character%2C%20they%20are%20obviously%20better%20judges%20of%20human%20character.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHimachal%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Sukhvinder%20Singh%20Sukhu%20said%20that%20of%20the%20nine%20MLAs%20who%20cross%20voted%2C%20three%20were%20independents%20and%20he%20did%20not%20want%20to%20comment%20on%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSix%20of%20them%20(who%20were%20elected%20as%20MLAs)%20sold%20their%20souls.%20They%20had%20defeated%20BJP%20candidates%20in%20their%20constituencies%20and%20come.%20And%20here%20they%20have%20voted%20against%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20candidate.%20Do%20you%20think%20this%20is%20because%20of%20being%20upset%3F%20This%20was%20not%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20culture.%20There%20have%20been%20disagreements%20but%20they%20have%20been%20elected%2C%20they%20have%20changed%20their%20vote%20and%20sold%20their%20souls.%20But%20people%20of%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20know%20that%20we%20have%20elected%20a%20Congress%20government%20for%20five%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%20reporters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20defeat%2C%20the%20party%20is%20possibly%20staring%20at%20an%20impending%20no%20confidence%20motion%20in%20the%20house%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20has%20already%20sought%20Sukhu%E2%80%99s%20resignation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20great%20victory.%20We%20were%20thinking%20whether%20we%20should%20fight%20at%20all%20because%20we%20were%20only%2025.%20But%20our%20party%20took%20a%20decision%20that%20despite%20wins%20and%20losses%20we%20must%20fight%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20former%20chief%20minister%20and%20leader%20of%20opposition%20BJP%20Jairam%20Thakur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20happy%20that%20we%20reached%20from%2025%20to%2034%20and%20then%20won%20by%20one%20vote.%20I%20congratulate%20our%20candidate%20Harsh%20Mahajan%20for%20winning.%20I%20am%20also%20grateful%20to%20all%20MLAs%20who%20listened%20to%20the%20voice%20of%20their%20conscience%2C%20whether%20it%20was%20from%20the%20BJP%20or%20Congress%20or%20independents%2C%20who%20voted%20for%20Mahajan.%20I%20want%20to%20say%20that%20following%20this%20result%2C%20Congress%E2%80%99%20chief%20minister%20should%20resign%20as%20he%20has%20no%20moral%20right%20to%20continue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EKarnataka%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20cross%20voting%20went%20against%20the%20Congress%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20it%20benefited%20from%20it%20in%20Karnataka%20where%20the%20party%20is%20also%20in%20power.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFour%20seats%20were%20up%20for%20election%20in%20the%20state%2C%20with%20five%20candidates%20in%20the%20fray%20after%20JD(S)%20named%20D.%20Kupendra%20Reddy%20on%20the%20last%20day%20of%20filing%20nominations.%20Earlier%20the%20Congress%20named%20three%20candidates%20including%20Ajay%20Maken%2C%20G.C.%20Chandrashekhar%20and%20Syed%20Nasir%20Hussain%20while%20the%20BJP%20had%20named%20Narayansa%20Bhandage%20as%20its%20candidate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20results%20which%20saw%20all%20three%20Congress%20candidates%20winning%20along%20with%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Bhandage%2C%20Congress%E2%80%99%20Karnataka%20in-charge%20Randeep%20Singh%20Surjewala%20said%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdecisive%20victory.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20laud%20the%20efforts%2C%20commitment%20to%20ideology%2C%20principles%20and%20democracy%20of%20the%20Congress%20legislators%20and%20all%20other%20supporting%20legislators%20who%20made%20this%20victory%20possible.%20This%20is%20a%20decisive%20victory%20for%20democracy%2C%20India%20and%20the%20self-respect%20of%20Kannadigas%20and%20a%20decisive%20defeat%20of%20those%20who%20want%20to%20corrupt%20the%20legislative%20process%20by%20sale%20and%20purchase%20of%20legislators%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%20reporters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20elections%2C%20BJP%20MLA%20S.T.%20Somashekar%20voted%20for%20Maken%2C%20while%20another%20BJP%20MLA%20A.%20Shivaram%20Hebbar%20abstained.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFollowing%20the%20results%2C%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20chief%20whip%20and%20former%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20R.%20Ashok%20said%20to%20reporters%20that%20legal%20action%20may%20be%20initiated%20against%20Somashekhar%2C%20reported%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20consulted%20with%20advocate%20Vivek%20Reddy%20who%20is%20our%20state%20legal%20cell%20president%20and%20a%20high%20court%20lawyer.%20We%20will%20ask%20the%20Speaker%20to%20initiate%20action%20against%20him%20(Somashekar)%20and%20explore%20the%20possibilities%20to%20take%20steps%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20Hebbar%20had%20%E2%80%9Cdouble-crossed%E2%80%9D%20the%20party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHebbar%20had%20been%20telling%20me%20that%20he%20would%20not%20betray%20the%20party%2C%20but%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20why%20he%20did%20not%20turn%20up%20to%20vote.%20He%20double-crossed%20us%20today%2C%20which%20he%20should%20not%20have%20done.%20We%20will%20initiate%20action%20against%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20135%20MLAs%20while%20the%20BJP%20has%2066%20and%20the%20JD(S)%2019%20MLAs%20in%20the%20assembly%20and%20each%20candidate%20needed%2045%20votes%20to%20win.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EUttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20eight%20of%20the%2010%20seats%20that%20were%20up%20for%20elections%20while%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20won%20two.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20both%20parties%20were%20set%20to%20get%20all%20their%20candidates%20(seven%20from%20the%20BJP%20and%20three%20from%20the%20SP)%20elected%2C%20the%20BJP%20threw%20a%20spanner%20into%20the%20works%20by%20naming%20an%20eighth%20candidate-on%20the%20last%20day%20of%20filing%20nominations-opening%20the%20doors%20for%20cross%20voting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20candidates%20include%20R.P.N.%20Singh%2C%20Navin%20Jain%2C%20Sangeeta%20Balwant%2C%20Sadhna%20Singh%2C%20Amarpal%20Maurya%2C%20Tejveer%20Singh%2C%20Sudhanshu%20Trivedi%20and%20industrialist%20Sanjay%20Seth%20who%20was%20named%20on%20the%20last%20day%20of%20filing%20nominations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Samajwadi%20Party%20candidates%20included%20Jaya%20Bachchan%2C%20Ramji%20Lal%20Suman%20and%20Alok%20Ranjan%20who%20lost%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20cross%20voting%20from%20SP%20MLAs%20with%20the%20day%20beginning%20with%20party%E2%80%99s%20chief%20whip%20Manoj%20Kumar%20Panday%20resigning%20from%20his%20post.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20one%20is%20in%20politics%2C%20one%20has%20to%20bear%20all%20kinds%20of%20blame.%20I%20have%20been%20nominated%20for%20the%20people%2C%20and%20I%20will%20think%20only%20about%20my%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%20reporters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%20party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20said%20that%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20those%20who%20vote%20against%20party%20lines.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNot%20everybody%20has%20the%20guts%20to%20stand%20against%20the%20government.%20Pressure%20is%20put%20on%20everybody%2C%20is%20there%20anyone%20who%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20know%20that%20BJP%20would%20go%20to%20any%20extent%20to%20win%3F%20BJP%20was%20dishonest%20during%20Chandigarh%20(mayor)%20elections%20also.%20As%20far%20as%20UP%20is%20concerned%2C%20BJP%20did%20everything%20to%20get%20votes%20and%20those%20who%20have%20left%2C%20may%20not%20have%20had%20the%20courage%20to%20stand%20against%20the%20BJP.%20Action%20will%20be%20taken%20because%20our%20party%20wants%20such%20people%20to%20be%20kept%20away%20from%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%20reporters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERanjan%20said%20to%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20that%20he%20had%20got%2019%20votes%20while%20the%20other%20two%20SP%20candidates-Bachchan%20and%20Suman%20got%2041%20and%2040%20votes%20respectively.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E37%20votes%20were%20needed%20by%20each%20candidate%20to%20win%20from%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20results%20were%20announced%20all%20eight%20BJP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%20were%20congratulated%20by%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%2C%20state%20BJP%20president%20Bhupendra%20Singh%20Chaudhary%20and%20deputy%20chief%20ministers%20Keshav%20Prasad%20Maurya%20and%20Brajesh%20Pathak%20for%20registering%20a%20%E2%80%9C