https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68420519%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Joe%20Biden's%20expected%20win%20comes%20despite%20a%20protest%20vote%20in%20the%20state%20over%20his%20stance%20on%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A60%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68420519%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68420519.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68420519.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian-American%20Jeweller%20Charged%20In%20Multi-Million%20Dollar%20Trade%20Fraud%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20Indian%20jeweller%20has%20been%20indicted%20for%20illegally%20evading%20customs%20duties%20for%20millions%20of%20dollars%20of%20jewellery%20imports%20into%20the%20US%20and%20operating%20unlicensed%20money%20transmitting%20businesses%2C%20a%20US%20attorney%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonishkumar%20Kirankumar%20Doshi%20Shah%20(39)%20--%20based%20out%20of%20both%20Mumbai%20and%20New%20Jersey%20--was%20arrested%20over%20the%20weekend%20and%20appeared%20on%20February%2026%20before%20US%20Magistrate%20Judge%20Andr%C3%A9%20M%20Espinosa%20in%20the%20Newark%20federal%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20alias%20%26quot%3BMonish%20Doshi%20Shah%26quot%3B%20was%20released%20on%20a%20bond%20of%20USD%20100%2C000%2C%20with%20home%20detention%20and%20location%20monitoring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20been%20charged%20on%20a%20complaint%20with%20one%20count%20of%20conspiracy%20to%20commit%20wire%20fraud%20and%20one%20count%20of%20operating%2C%20aiding%20and%20abetting%20the%20operation%20of%20an%20unlicensed%20money%20transmitting%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20January%202015%20through%20September%202023%2C%20Shah%20engaged%20in%20a%20scheme%20to%20evade%20duties%20for%20shipments%20of%20jewellery%20from%20Turkey%20and%20India%20to%20the%20US%2C%20according%20to%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20would%20ship%20or%20instruct%20his%20conspirators%20to%20ship%20goods%20from%20Turkey%20or%20India%2C%20which%20would%20have%20been%20subject%20to%20an%20approximately%205.5%20per%20cent%20duty%20if%20shipped%20directly%20to%20the%20US%2C%20to%20one%20of%20Shah's%20companies%20in%20South%20Korea%2C%20these%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFederal%20prosecutors%20alleged%20that%20Shah's%20conspirators%20in%20South%20Korea%20would%20change%20the%20labels%20on%20the%20jewellery%20to%20state%20that%20they%20were%20from%20South%20Korea%20instead%20of%20Turkey%20or%20India%2C%20and%20then%20ship%20them%20to%20Shah%20or%20his%20customers%20in%20the%20US%2C%20thereby%20unlawfully%20evading%20the%20duty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20would%20also%20make%20and%20instruct%20his%20customers%20to%20make%20fake%20invoices%20and%20packing%20lists%20to%20make%20it%20look%20like%20Shah's%20South%20Korean%20companies%20were%20actually%20ordering%20jewellery%20from%20Turkey%20or%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20scheme%2C%20Shah%20shipped%20millions%20of%20dollars%20of%20jewellery%20from%20South%20Korea%20to%20the%20US%2C%20prosecutors%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20July%202020%20through%20November%202021%2C%20Shah%20operated%20numerous%20purported%20jewellery%20companies%20in%20New%20York%20City's%20Diamond%20District%2C%20including%20MKore%20LLC%20(MKore)%2C%20MKore%20USA%20Inc.%20(MKore%20USA)%20and%20Vruman%20Corp%20(Vruman)%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20used%20these%20entities%20to%20conduct%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20illegal%20financial%20transactions%20for%20customers%2C%20including%20converting%20cash%20to%20checks%20or%20wire%20transfers%2C%20the%20documents%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20would%20also%20collect%20cash%20from%20customers%20and%20use%20conspirators'%20jewellery%20companies%2C%20also%20located%20in%20the%20Diamond%20District%2C%20to%20convert%20the%20cash%20into%20wires%20or%20checks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20documents%20said%20that%20at%20times%2C%20Shah%20and%20his%20conspirators%20moved%20more%20than%20a%20million%20dollars%20of%20cash%20in%20a%20single%20day.%20In%20exchange%20for%20their%20services%2C%20Shah%20and%20his%20conspirators%20charged%20a%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20said%20that%20none%20of%20Shah's%20or%20his%20conspirators'%20companies%20were%20registered%20as%20money%20transmitting%20businesses%20with%20New%20York%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20or%20the%20Financial%20Crimes%20Enforcement%20Network%20(FinCEN).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709089740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-07%2Fatt9hsso_court-generic_625x300_27_July_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-american-jeweller-charged-in-multi-million-dollar-international-trade-fraud-5141001%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Indian%20jeweller%20has%20been%20indicted%20for%20illegally%20evading%20customs%20duties%20for%20millions%20of%20dollars%20of%20jewellery%20imports%20into%20the%20US%20and%20operating%20unlicensed%20money%20transmitting%20businesses%2C%20a%20US%20attorney%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-american-jeweller-charged-in-multi-million-dollar-international-trade-fraud-5141001%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-american-jeweller-charged-in-multi-million-dollar-international-trade-fraud-5141001%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Findian-american-jeweller-charged-in-multi-million-dollar-international-trade-fraud-5141001%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22W