tting%20line-up.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEngland's%20senior%20batters%20including%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ben%20Stokes%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1434-ben-stokes-playerprofile%5C%22%3EBen%20Stokes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jonny%20Bairstow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1551-jonny-bairstow-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJonny%20Bairstow%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Joe%20Root%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1433-joe-root-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJoe%20Root%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20other%20than%20the%20Ranchi%20Test%2C%20didn't%20contribute%20consistently.%20There%20were%20some%20key%20moments%20that%20they%20grabbed%20on%20a%20couple%20of%20occasions%20but%20other%20key%20moments%20they%20let%20go.%20It's%20all%20nice%20to%20say%20that%20%E2%80%98this%20is%20the%20way%20I%20bat'%2C%20but%20you%20can't%20bat%20like%20that%20all%20the%20time.%20You%20have%20to%20hold%20back.%20In%20Test%20match%20cricket%2C%20that's%20what%20it%20is.%20It's%20about%20situations%20and%20that's%20what%20Root%20did%20in%20this%20(Ranchi)%20match.%20No%20wonder%20he%20was%20successful%2C%20something%20that%20England%20will%20have%20to%20discuss%20and%20look%20at.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Aakash%20Chopra%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F597-aakash-chopra-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAakash%20Chopra%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20JioCinema%20and%20Sports18%20expert%2C%20also%20gave%20his%20ingihht%20on%20the%20impact%20of%20Bazball%20in%20the%20series%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20match%20took%20everyone%20by%20surprise.%20We%20had%20heard%20of%20Bazball%2C%20but%20had%20not%20seen%20it.%20That%20you%20are%20behind%20by%20190%20runs%20on%20a%20turning%20pitch%20and%20then%20you%20employ%20sweep%2C%20reverse%20sweep%2C%20reverse%20hit%20and%20suddenly%20you%20react%2C%20%E2%80%98wow%2C%20cricket%20can%20be%20played%20in%20such%20a%20way.'%20That%20was%20our%20introduction%20to%20Bazball.%20After%20that%2C%20England%20found%20themselves%20in%20many%20situations%20from%20where%20they%20could%20have%20closed%20matches.%20I%20remember%20Joe%20Root's%20shot%20from%20the%20Rajkot%20match.%20England%20had%20completely%20dominated%20the%20last%20session%20of%20the%20previous%20day's%20play.%20They%20needed%20to%20just%20consolidate%20after%20that%2C%20but%20they%20didn't%20do%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20I%20feel%2C%20if%20England%20do%20an%20honest%20assessment%2C%20they%20would%20feel%2C%20Root%20should%20play%20the%20way%20he%20has%20all%20his%20career.%20There%20are%20some%20basic%20principles%20of%20cricket%20that%20have%20not%20changed.%20Bazball%20should%20not%20be%20used%20as%20a%20cop-up%2C%20saying%20that%20this%20is%20the%20way%20we%20play.%20If%20that's%20the%20way%20you%20are%20going%20to%20play%2C%20then%20score%20a%20century%20and%20not%2025.%20If%20you%20can't%20score%20that%20ton%2C%20then%20please%20play%20some%20other%20way.%20This%20logic%20applies%20to%20Jonny%20Bairstow%20and%20Ben%20Stokes.%20Please%20score%20runs%20on%20good%20batting%20surfaces%2C%20and%20give%20it%20whatever%20name%20you%20want.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20series%20certainly%20proved%20that%20England%20played%20an%20entertaining%20brand%20of%20cricket.%20But%20the%20success%20that%20their%20most%20successful%20batsman%20got%20in%20the%20end%20was%20through%20playing%20orthodox%2C%20conventional%20Test%20cricket%20that's%20being%20played%20for%20over%20150%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709087940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fs9un91h8_england-tests_625x300_12_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2024%2Fbazball-or-whatever-ball-you-call-it-india-greats-dig-at-ben-stokes-and-cos-misfiring-england-5139378%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Though%20England%20looke