showed%20interest%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20an%20interview.%20Kim%20said%20he's%20met%20eight%20securities%20firms%20and%20banks%20dealing%20with%20local%20retails%20investor%20this%20year%20with%20inquiries%20about%20India's%20bond%20market%2C%20compared%20with%20virtually%20none%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20US%20stocks%20have%20been%20in%20the%20spotlight%2C%20with%20the%20rally%20to%20records%20playing%20out%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20a%20still-nascent%20recovery%20in%20Chinese%20equities.%20Even%20Japan's%20retail%20investors%2C%20who%20have%20traditionally%20been%20inclined%20toward%20the%20US%2C%20are%20showing%20interest%20in%20the%20South%20Asian%20nation%20that%20boasts%20the%20fastest%20growth%20rate%20among%20the%20major%20economies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20hottest%20topic%20is%20certainly%20the%20US%20these%20days%2C%20but%20outside%20of%20US%20assets%2C%20India%20is%20gaining%20attention%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Cho%20Jae%20Sung%2C%20general%20manager%20of%20Shinhan%20Bank's%20Seoyeouido%20branch%20in%20Seoul.%20The%20interest%20is%20mainly%20from%20those%20who%20prefer%20funds%20and%20are%20looking%20for%20better%20returns%2C%20Cho%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shift%20comes%20as%20China%20grapples%20with%20ongoing%20economic%20challenges%2C%20while%20India's%20sovereign%20bonds%20are%20set%20to%20be%20added%20to%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20%26amp%3B%20Co.'s%20global%20debt%20indexes%20from%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20inclusion%20is%20expected%20to%20lure%20up%20to%20%2430%20billion%20of%20inflows%2C%20which%20exceeds%20the%20size%20of%20Indian%20sovereign%20bonds%20currently%20held%20by%20foreigners%2C%20Kim%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20appeal%20of%20investing%20in%20India%20is%20also%20due%20to%20its%20stable%20currency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rupee%20is%20Asia's%20top%20performer%20this%20year%2C%20up%200.4%25%20versus%20the%20dollar%20with%20the%20lowest%20volatility%20among%20emerging%20market%20currencies%2C%20according%20to%20data%20compiled%20by%20Bloomberg.%20The%20South%20Korean%20won%20has%20weakened%203.2%25%20in%20the%20same%20period%2C%20after%20gaining%204.8%25%20in%20the%20fourth%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKim%2C%20who%20has%20been%20managing%20the%20India%20fund%20since%202013%2C%20said%20he%20prefers%20investing%20in%20rupee%20bonds%20issued%20by%20supranational%20organizations.%20The%20securities%20make%20up%2040%25%20of%20the%20fund%2C%20with%20the%20rest%20allocated%20to%20debt%20issued%20by%20the%20nation's%20state%20companies%2C%20the%20country's%20treasuries%20and%20currency%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20plans%20to%20increase%20the%20fund's%20current%20duration%20of%202.7%25%20considering%20the%20prospect%20of%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20cutting%20rates%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fund%20has%20returned%209.3%25%20through%20the%20past%2012%20months%20as%20of%20Monday%2C%20and%20almost%206%25%20annually%20over%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20data%20compiled%20by%20Bloomberg%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709086800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2F06mvn7ao_100-and-500-rupee-notes-currency-notes_625x300_14_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Findias-booming-bond-market-attracts-south-korean-investors-5141145%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20craze%20for%20India's%20booming%20bond%20market%20has%20reached%20as%20far%20as%20South%20Korea%2C%20where%20a%20bond%20fund%20that's%20been%20mostly%20dormant%20for%20a%20decade%20is%20suddenly%20getting%20lots%20of%20interest.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Findias-booming-bond-mark