%20solar-charging%20capability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntuitive%20Machines%20said%20the%20next%20day%20that%20human%20error%20was%20to%20blame%20for%20the%20navigational%20issue.%20Flight%20readiness%20teams%20had%20neglected%20to%20manually%20unlock%20a%20safety%20switch%20before%20launch%2C%20preventing%20subsequent%20activation%20of%20the%20vehicle's%20laser-guided%20range%20finders%20and%20forcing%20flight%20engineers%20to%20hurriedly%20improvise%20an%20alternative%20during%20lunar%20orbit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Intuitive%20executive%20told%20Reuters%20on%20Saturday%20that%20the%20safety%20switch%20lapse%20stemmed%20from%20the%20company's%20decision%20to%20forgo%20a%20test-firing%20of%20the%20laser%20system%20during%20pre-launch%20checks%20in%20order%20to%20save%20time%20and%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20or%20not%20failure%20of%20the%20range%20finders%20and%20last-minute%20substitution%20of%20a%20work-around%20ultimately%20caused%20Odysseus%20to%20land%20in%20an%20off-kilter%20manner%20remained%20an%20open%20question%2C%20according%20to%20Intuitive%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20the%20company%20said%20last%20Friday%20that%20two%20of%20the%20spacecraft's%20communication%20antennae%20were%20knocked%20out%20of%20commission%2C%20pointed%20the%20wrong%20way%2C%20and%20that%20its%20solar%20panels%20were%20likewise%20facing%20the%20wrong%20direction%2C%20limiting%20the%20vehicle's%20ability%20to%20recharge%20its%20batteries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20consequence%2C%20Intuitive%20said%20on%20Monday%20that%20it%20expected%20to%20lose%20contact%20with%20Odysseus%20on%20Tuesday%20morning%2C%20cutting%20short%20the%20mission%20that%20held%20a%20dozen%20science%20instruments%20for%20NASA%20and%20several%20commercial%20customers%20and%20had%20been%20intended%20to%20operate%20on%20the%20moon%20for%20seven%20to%2010%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBeside%20Crater%20Wall%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%20morning%2C%20Intuitive%20said%20controllers%20were%20still%20%26quot%3Bworking%20on%20final%20determination%20of%20battery%20life%20on%20the%20lander%2C%20which%20may%20continue%20up%20to%20an%20additional%2010-20%20hours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20update%20from%20the%20company%20indicated%20the%20spacecraft%20might%20last%20for%20a%20total%20of%20six%20days%20before%20the%20sun%20sets%20over%20the%20landing%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20shares%20were%20down%208%25%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20paring%20losses%20after%20Intuitive%20said%20it%20was%20still%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20lander.%20Still%2C%20the%20stock%20has%20wiped%20out%20most%20of%20its%20gain%20since%20late%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20remained%20to%20be%20seen%20how%20much%20research%20data%20and%20imagery%20from%20various%20payloads%20might%20go%20uncollected%20because%20of%20Odysseus'%20cockeyed%20landing%20and%20shortened%20lunar%20lifespan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENASA%20paid%20Intuitive%20%24118%20million%20to%20build%20and%20fly%20Odysseus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENASA%20chief%20Bill%20Nelson%20told%20Reuters%20on%20Tuesday%20he%20understood%20that%20agency%20scientists%20expected%20to%20retrieve%20some%20data%20from%20all%20six%20of%20their%20payloads.%20He%20also%20said%20Odysseus%20apparently%20landed%20beside%20a%20crater%20wall%20and%20was%20leaning%20at%20a%2012-degree%20angle%2C%20though%20it%20was%20not%20clear%20whether%20that%20meant%2012%20degrees%20from%20the%20surface%20or%2012%20degrees%20from%20an%20upright%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntuitive%20executives%20said%20on%20Feb.%2023%20that%20engineers%20believed%20Odysseus%20had%20caught%20the%20foot%20of%20one%20of%20its%20landing%20legs%20on%20the%20lunar%20surface%20as%20it%20neared%20touchdown%20and%20tipped%20over%20before%20coming%20to%20rest%20horizontally%2C%20apparently%20propped%20up%20on%20a%20rock.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20photos%20f