22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fentire-country-taken-for-a-ride-sc-temporarily-bans-patanjali-medicine-ads-124022701015_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fentire-country-taken-for-a-ride-sc-temporarily-bans-patanjali-medicine-ads-124022701015_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Only%20A%20Few%20Muslim%20MLAs%20Will%20Remain%20In%20Assam%20Congress%20By%202026%3A%20Himanta%20Sarma%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAssam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20on%20Tuesday%20remarked%20that%20by%20the%20time%20the%202026%20assembly%20election%20arrives%2C%20only%20a%20few%20Muslim%20MLAs%20would%20remain%20in%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20MLAs%20such%20as%20Rakibul%20Hussain%2C%20Rekibuddin%20Ahmed%2C%20Jakir%20Hussain%20Sikdar%2C%20Nurul%20Huda%20and%20a%20few%20more%20will%20remain%20in%20the%20party%2C%20Mr%20Sarma%20told%20reporters%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20a%20programme%20at%20Gohpur%20in%20Bishwanath%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20Congress%20leader%20Rana%20Goswami%2C%20who%20resigned%20as%20its%20working%20president%20recently%2C%20is%20joining%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%20he%20has%20no%20information%20about%20it.%20%26quot%3BHe%20is%20a%20powerful%20leader%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20if%20he%20joins%20the%20BJP%2C%20I%20will%20welcome%20it%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20politician%2C%20however%2C%20has%20to%20consider%20many%20aspects%20before%20taking%20a%20decision%2C%20Mr%20Sarma%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEchoing%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20the%20state%20Water%20Resources%20Minister%20Pijush%20Hazarika%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BExcept%20the%20names%20I%20mentioned%2C%20all%20other%20Congress%20leaders%20and%20MLAs%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20us%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Assam%20Pradesh%20Congress%20(PCC)%20Chief%20Bhupen%20Borah%20had%20claimed%20that%20Mr%20Sarma%20was%20afraid%20of%20him%20as%20is%20evident%20from%20his%20%26quot%3Bacrimonious%20behaviour%20towards%20me%20and%20family%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Borah%20alleged%20that%20his%20brother%20and%20sister-in-law%2C%20both%20government%20employees%2C%20have%20been%20transferred%20to%20two%20opposite%20corners%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PCC%20chief%20further%20said%20he%20had%20asked%20for%20increased%20security%20after%20he%20was%20assaulted%20during%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20in%20January%2C%20but%20that%20has%20not%20been%20given%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20state%20president%20also%20alleged%20that%20those%20who%20''physically%20attacked%20me%20during%20the%20%23BharatJodoNyayYatra%20are%20being%20allowed%20to%20roam%20free''.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''In%20a%20state%20where%20writing%20a%20poem%20of%20dissent%2C%20or%20a%20scathing%20tweet%2C%20can%20get%20you%20arrested%2C%20just%20imagine%20an%20assailant%20walking%20about%20freely%2C%20without%20a%20care%20in%20the%20world!''%2C%20he%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Acrimony%20is%20a%20sign%20of%20fear!%20I%20am%20certain%20that%20if%20there%20is%20one%20person%20in%20Assam%20that%20%40HimantaBiswa%20truly%20fears%2C%20it%20is%20me.%20Why%3F%20Because%20his%20acrimonious%20behaviour%20towards%20me%20and%20my%20family%20betrays%20his%20innermost%20fears%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20leader%20asserted%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%20''can%20buy%20a%20few%20MLAs%20here%20and%20there%2C%20but%20he%20cannot%20buy%20me''.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Just%20see%20his%20acrimonious%20behaviour%20towards%20me%20and%20my%20family%3A%20He%20transferred%20out%20my%20brother%20and%20sister-in-law%2C%20both%20government%20servants%2C%20to%20two%20opposite%20corners%20of%20Assam.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20is%20safe%20to%20say%3A%20fear%2C%20thy%20name%20is%20Himanta!''%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20Mr%20Borah's%20allegation%2C%20Water%20Resources%20Minister%20Pijush%20Hazarika%20said%20that%20government%20employees%20must%20serve%20in%20any%20corner%20of%20the%20state%20and%20he%20cannot%20concern%20himself%20with%20the%20Congress%20leader's%20sense%20of%20entitlement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Just%20because%20they%20happen%20to%20be%20relatives%20of%20some%20big%20Congress%20leader%2C%20doesn't%20mean%20they%20will%20get%20special%20treatment%2C''%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709059320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fu743q1go_himanta-biswa-sarma_625x300_11_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fonly-a-few-muslim-mlas-will-remain-in-assam-congress-before-2026-polls-himanta-biswa-sarma-5139770%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Assam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20on%20Tuesday%20remarked%20that%20by%20the%20time%20the%202026%20assembly%20election%20arrives%2C%20only%20a%20few%20Muslim%20MLAs%20would%20remain%20in%20the%20Congress.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fonly-a-few-muslim-mlas-will-remain-in-assam-congress-before-2026-polls-himanta-biswa-sarma-5139770%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fonly-a-few-muslim-mlas-will-remain-in-assam-congress-before-2026-polls-himanta-biswa-sarma-5139770%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fonly-a-few-muslim-mlas-will-remain-in-assam-congress-before-2026-polls-himanta-biswa-sarma-5139770%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vodafone%20Idea%20plans%20to%20raise%20up%20