ajwadi%20Party%20Two%20In%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Polls%20In%20Uttar%20Pradesh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20pulled%20off%20a%20stunning%20extra%20seat%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20today%20--%20with%20some%20help%20from%20Jayant%20Chaudhary's%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20and%20a%20handful%20of%20Samajwadi%20Party%20rebels.%20The%20party%20won%20eight%20of%20the%20state's%2010%20seats%2C%20two%20went%20to%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20which%20was%20expecting%20three.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20bonus%20seat%20won%20by%20the%20BJP%20was%20in%20Congress-ruled%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20with%20cross-voting%20by%20six%20Congress%20MLAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20forced%20an%20election%20by%20fielding%20an%20eighth%20candidate%20for%20the%20state's%2010%20seats.%20The%20numbers%20decreed%20that%20seven%20seats%20would%20go%20to%20the%20BJP%20and%20three%20to%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party.%3Cbr%3E%5CnBut%20as%20early%20as%20yesterday%2C%20BJP%20leaders%20started%20claiming%20in%20private%20that%20a%20clutch%20of%20Samajwadi%20Party%20MLAs%20would%20cross-vote%20today.%20The%20numbers%20quoted%20varied%20between%207%20and%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20late%20evening%2C%20the%20writing%20was%20on%20the%20wall%2C%20with%20eight%20MLAs%20staying%20away%20from%20a%20meeting%20called%20by%20party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav.%20This%20morning%2C%20ahead%20of%20elections%2C%20the%20party's%20chief%20whip%20resigned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actual%20voting%20today%20was%20replete%20with%20suspense%20and%20drama%2C%20as%20seven%20members%20of%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20cross-voted.%20The%20vote%20of%20one%20SP%20MLA%20was%20deemed%20invalid.%20After%20the%20voting%2C%20five%20Samajwadi%20Party%20MPs%20met%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20eight%20BJP%20candidates%20who%20won%20are%20former%20Union%20Minister%20RPN%20Singh%2C%20former%20MP%20Chaudhary%20Tejveer%20Singh%2C%20Amarpal%20Maurya%2C%20Sangeeta%20Balwant%20%2C%20BJP%20spokesperson%20Sudhanshu%20Trivedi%2C%20former%20MLA%20Sadhna%20Singh%2C%20Naveen%20Jain%20and%20Sanjay%20Seth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamajwadi%20Party's%20Jaya%20Bachchan%20and%20Ramji%20Lal%20Suman%20won.%20Alok%20Ranjan%2C%20the%20third%20candidate%20fielded%20by%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20lost%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20been%20saying%20from%20the%20beginning%20that%20all%208%20candidates%20of%20the%20BJP%20will%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Keshav%20Pradhan%20Maurya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20congratulate%20all%20the%20winning%20candidates.%20Two%20SP%20candidates%20have%20also%20won.%20So%2C%20congratulations%20to%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20too.%20BJP's%20vijay%20yatra%20that%20began%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20will%20continue%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20then%20go%20on%20till%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20even%20further%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESP%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20said%20disciplinary%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20MLAs%20if%20they%20had%20cross%20voted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20everybody%20has%20the%20guts%20to%20stand%20against%20the%20government.%20Pressure%20is%20put%20on%20everybody%2C%20is%20there%20anyone%20who%20doesn't%20know%20that%20BJP%20would%20go%20to%20any%20extent%20to%20win%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20was%20dishonest%20during%20the%20Chandigarh%20elections%20also...%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20UP%2C%20BJP%20did%20everything%20to%20get%20votes%20and%20those%20who%20left%2C%20might%20not%20have%20had%20the%20guts%20to%20stand%20against%20the%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shock%20defeat%20was%20a%20blow%20for%20Opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%2C%20which%20was%20looking%20for%20two%20more%20seats%20in%20the%20Upper%20House%20in%20this%20round%20of%20election.%20The%20NDA%20is%20inching%20towards%20majority%20in%20the%20245-member%20Rajya%20Sabha%20%E2%80%93%20crucial%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20passing%20or%20blocking%20of%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709057280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F12k0a51_yogi-rajya-sabha-wins_625x300_27_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-wins-8-seats-samajwadi-party-two-in-rajya-sabha-polls-in-uttar-pradesh-5139209%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20pulled%20off%20a%20stunning%20extra%20seat%20for%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20today%2C%20with%20some%20help%20from%20Jayant%20Chaudhary's%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20and%20a%20handful%20of%20Samajwadi%20Party%20rebels.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-wins-8-seats-samajwadi-party-two-in-rajya-sabha-polls-in-uttar-pradesh-5139209%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-wins-8-seats-samajwadi-party-two-in-rajya-sabha-polls-in-uttar-pradesh-5139209%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-wins-8-seats-samajwadi-party-two-in-rajya-sabha-polls-in-uttar-pradesh-5139209%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20York%20medical%20school%20scraps%20fees%20after%20%241%20bn%20donation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709057168000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108052047%2Cimgsize-2065488.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fnew-york-medical-school-scraps-fees-after-1-bn-donation%2Farticleshow%2F108052012.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108052012.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EA%20New%20York%20medical%20school%20will%20