0do%20anything.%20This%20government%20won%E2%80%99t%20go%20on%2C%20it%20will%20topple%20with%20its%20own%20weight.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20indicated%20that%20suspense%20is%20not%20over%20in%20Himachal%E2%80%99s%20politics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%20in%20a%20first%20reaction%2C%20Singhvi%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CFirst%20of%20all%2C%20I%20extend%20heartiest%20congratulations%20to%20Harsh%20Mahajan.%20But%20I%20would%20like%20to%20tell%20his%20party%2C%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%93%20introspect%20and%20think.%20When%20a%2025-member%20party%20fields%20a%20candidate%20against%20a%2043-member%20party%2C%20there%20is%20just%20one%20message%20%E2%80%93%20we%20will%20shamelessly%20do%20everything%20which%20is%20not%20permitted%20by%20the%20law%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20be%20living%20in%20a%20fool%E2%80%99s%20paradise%20if%20we%20think%20that%20alll%20those%20MLAs%20%5Bwho%20cross-voted%5D%20had%20a%20sudden%20change%20of%20heart%20due%20to%20some%20ideology%20or%20new%20policy.%20This%20is%20rather%20disappointing%20and%20something%20this%20hilly%20state%20has%20never%20seen%20before%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singhvi%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Mahajan%20dedicated%20his%20victory%20to%20top%20BJP%20leaders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20opposition%20Jai%20Ram%20Thakur%20will%20reportedly%20meet%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20governor%20tomorrow%20and%20has%20sought%20Sukhu%E2%80%99s%20resignation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMany%20aspect%20to%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20defeat%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20defeat%20has%20many%20aspects.%20Some%20speculate%20that%20it%20was%20the%20outcome%20of%20infighting%20between%20Sukhu%20and%20Himachal%20Congress%20chief%20Pratibha%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20wife%20of%20the%20late%20Congress%20stalwart%20Virbhadra%20Singh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20victory%20in%20the%202022%20assembly%20polls%2C%20Pratibha%20staked%20a%20claim%20on%20the%20CM%20post%2C%20which%20went%20to%20Sukhu%20as%20the%20Congress%20went%20for%20a%20generation%20shift%20after%20eight-time%20CM%20Virbhadra%E2%80%99s%20death.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20then%2C%20their%20differences%20have%C2%A0%20cropped%20up%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20several%20times.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20speculation%20becomes%20more%20rife%20because%20most%20MLAs%20who%20cross-voted%20in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20favour%20were%20once%20staunch%20supporters%20of%20Virbhadra.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20people%20also%20believed%20that%20some%20MLAs%20were%20upset%20with%20Sukhu%20for%20not%20giving%20them%20plum%20postings%20in%20the%20government%20and%20that%20these%20MLAs%20had%20humiliated%20the%20party%2C%20especially%20in%20light%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20are%20round%20the%20corner.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApart%20from%20this%2C%20Mahajan%20%E2%80%93%20the%20winning%20candidate%20%E2%80%93%20is%20an%20old%20Congress%20veteran%20who%20too%20had%20close%20relations%20with%20Virbhadra%20at%20one%20point%20of%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20might%20have%20helped%20him%20swing%20many%20of%20his%20close%20associates%20to%20his%20side%20after%20the%20BJP%20fielded%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMahajan%2C%20who%20is%20also%20former%20working%20president%20of%20the%20Himachal%20Congress%20and%20a%20former%20cabinet%20minister%2C%20joined%20the%20BJP%20two%20months%20before%20the%20state%20assembly%20polls%20in%20November%202022.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709054099000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F49_Image8.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fhimac