p%3EHe%20added%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20claims%20on%20the%20economic%20front%20%E2%80%9Care%20not%20supported%20by%20data%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20Thomas%20Piketty%2C%20Jaffrelot%20said%20India%20is%20the%20most%20unequal%20country%20in%20the%20world%20after%20South%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20one%20point%20in%20the%20interview%20he%20described%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20economic%20policies%20as%20%E2%80%9Cpro-rich%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20attitude%20to%20Muslims%2C%20Jaffrelot%20said%20%E2%80%9Che%20looks%20at%20Muslims%20as%20descendants%20of%20converts%20or%20foreigners%E2%80%9D.%20Jaffrelot%20said%20he%20treats%20them%20as%20second-class%20citizens%20who%20should%20be%20%E2%80%98obliterated%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98ghettoised%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaffrelot%20said%20the%20majoritarian%20attitude%20means%20%E2%80%9CMuslims%20are%20at%20the%20bottom%20or%20margins%20of%20the%20social%20pyramid%E2%80%9D.%20He%20said%20%E2%80%9CMuslims%20are%20de%20facto%20second-class%20citizens%20becoming%20de%20jure%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20relation%20to%20a%20question%20about%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20participation%20in%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20consecration%2C%20when%20he%20emerged%20as%20the%20high-priest%20of%20Hindu%20nationalism%2C%20Jaffrelot%20said%20%E2%80%9Csecularism%20is%20dying%E2%80%9D.%20He%20called%20it%20%E2%80%9Ca%20dead%20letter%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20not%20Hinduism%20but%20%E2%80%9CHindutva%20is%20the%20de%20facto%20ideology%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20personality%20cult%20surrounding%20Modi%2C%20Jaffrelot%20first%20compared%20it%20to%20the%20personality%20cult%20under%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20but%20added%20that%20for%20two%20reasons%2C%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20personality%20cult%20is%20greater%20and%20also%20more%20disturbing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%20did%20not%20differentiate%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims.%20Second%2C%20she%20did%20not%20have%20access%20to%20the%20modern%20day%20technologies%20available%20to%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20Nehru%2C%20Jaffrelot%20said%20that%20he%20%E2%80%9Cthinks%E2%80%9D%20that%20Modi%20does%20have%20a%20complex%20about%20Nehru%2C%20who%20he%20is%20constantly%20targeting%20and%20belittling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaffrelot%20said%20that%20if%20Modi%20is%20re-elected%2C%20he%20does%20envisage%20definite%20steps%20being%20taken%20towards%20creating%20a%20Hindu%20%3Cem%3Erashtra%3C%2Fem%3E%20(nation).%20He%20says%20they%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20taken%20immediately%20after%20the%20re-election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20Jaffrelot%20said%20%E2%80%9CModi%20has%20no%20successor%E2%80%9D%2C%20adding%20%E2%80%9Cit%20is%20very%20difficult%20to%20succeed%20a%20man%20like%20Modi%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20understand%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20and%20political%20personality%2C%20I%20cannot%20strongly%20enough%20recommend%20this%20interview.%20Jaffrelot%20has%20spoken%20analytically%2C%20but%20also%20with%20illustrative%20detail.%20He%E2%80%99s%20measured%20but%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20critical.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsequently%2C%20the%20interview%20is%20a%20%3Cem%3Etour%20d%E2%80%99horizon%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20situation%20today%20as%20well%20as%20a%20perceptive%20analysis%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20personality%20and%20political%20qualities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWeeks%20before%20the%20next%20general%20election%2C%20I%20do%20believe%20this%20is%20an%20interview%20you%20must%20see%20to%20understand%20where%20we%20are%2C%20what%20sort%20of%20person%20is%20our%20prime%20minister%2C%20what%20are%20the%20implications%20of%20the%20policies%20he%E2%80%99s%20followed%2C%20their%20success%20or%20lack%20of%20and%2C%20at%20the%20end%2C%20what%20to%20expect%20if%20he%20wins%20as%20well%20as%20what%20to%20expect%20when%20he%20finally%20departs%20the%20political%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FsGRQOR0P4c8%3Fsi%3DL8GVJ1jU3CXGLIOY%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20you%2C%20I%20give%20below%20the%20list%20of%20questions%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20been%20prime%20minister%20for%20ten%20years%20and%20he%20hopes%20to%20add%20another%20five%20at%20the%20forthcoming%20elections.%20Let%20me%20start%20by%20asking%20what%20is%20your%20assessment%20of%20his%20performance%20as%20prime%20minister%20over%20the%20last%20decade%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E2.%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20frequently%20boasts%20of%20his%20handling%20of%20the%20economy.%20He%20says%20he%E2%80%99s%20made%20India%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20fifth-biggest%20economy%20and%20lifted%20250%20million%20out%20of%20poverty.%20His%20critics%20talk%20about%20unprecedented%20levels%20of%20unemployment%2C%20increasing%20inequality%20and%20K-shaped%20growth.%20What%E2%80%99s%20your%20opinion%20of%20how%20Modi%20has%20handled%20the%20economy%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E3.%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20dominates%20the%20Indian%20political%20horizon%20and%20there%20is%20a%20huge%20personality%20cult%20that%20surrounds%20him.%20He%20only%20refers%20to%20himself%20in%20the%20third%20person%20and%20often%20his%20ministers%20and%20even%20a%20former%20vice%20president%20compare%20him%20to%20God.%20His%20policies%20are%20called%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20guarantees.%20Is%20all%20of%20this%20understandable%20and%20justified%20or%20is%20it%20approaching%20megalomania%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E4.%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3ESide-by-side%20with%20the%20personality%20cult%20and%20larger-than-life%20image%20is%20his%20style%20of%20governance.%20How%20would%20you%20characterise%20his%20handling%20of%20institutions%20like%20parliament%2C%20the%20election%20commission%2C%20the%20judiciary%20and%20security%20agencies%20like%20the%20CBI%20and%20ED%3F%20And%20the%20fact%20everything%20is%20run%20by%20the%20PMO%2C%20not%20ministers%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20believes%20he%E2%80%99s%20deepened%20Indian%20democracy.%20His%20critics%20accuse%20him%20of%20authoritarianism.%20What%E2%80%99s%20your%20opinion%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cspan%3EOne%20deep%20concern%20is%20the%20sharp%20divide%20that%E2%80%99s%20emerged%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims.%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20vigorously%20deny%20this%2C%20but%20many%20believe%20they%20are%20responsible%20for%20it.%20What%E2%80%99s%20your%20view%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E6.%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20Modi%2C%20the%20BJP%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20single%20Muslim%20MP%20in%20either%20house%20of%20parliament.%20It%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20fielded%20a%20single%20Muslim%20candidate%20in%20states%20like%20UP%20and%20Karnataka%20with%20substantial%20Muslim%20populations%20and%20in%20Gujarat%20for%20over%2025%20years.%20BJP%20chief%20ministers%20and%20MPs%20call%20Muslims%20%3Cem%3EBabar%20ki%20aulad%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Babur%E2%80%99s%20offspring)%20and%20tell%20them%20to%20go%20to%20Pakistan.%20We%E2%80%99ve%20even%20had%20calls%20for%20a%20Muslim%20genocide.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERight%20through%20all%20of%20this%2C%20Modi%20has%20kept%20quiet.%20What%20does%20this%20tell%20us%20about%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20attitude%20to%20Muslims%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E7.%3C%2Fb%3E%20%3Cspan%3EOn%20January%2022%2C%20when%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20happened%2C%20Modi%20seemed%20to%20emerge%20as%20the%20high%20priest%20of%20Hindu%20nationalism.%20What%20is%20the%20likely%20impact%20of%20this%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20secularism%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20basic%20structure%20of%20the%20constitution%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E8.%3C%2Fb%3E%20%3Cspan%3EHow%20badly%20has%20the%20line%20that%20should%20separate%20religion%20and%20politics%20been%20breached%3F%20I%E2%80%99m%20referring%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Esengol%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20parliament%2C%20the%20constant%20references%20to%20Hinduism%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20speeches%20and%20his%20much%20publicised%20preparation%20for%20and%20role%20in%20the%20temple%20consecration.%20Is%20Hinduism%20becoming%20the%20de%20facto%20official%20religion%20of%20the%20country%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E9.%3C%2Fb%3E%20%3Cspan%3ECan%20this%20increasing%20Hinduisation%20be%20reversed%3F%20Can%20we%20go%20back%20to%20square%20one%3F%20Or%20is%20that%20unlikely%20if%20not%20impossible%3F%20After%20all%2C%20Zia%E2%80%99s%20Islamisation%20in%20Pakistan%20may%20be%20criticised%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20never%20been%20rolled%20back.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E10.%3C%2Fb%3E%20%3Cspan%3EModi%20repeatedly%20claims%20he%E2%80%99s%20made%20India%20great%20again.%20He%20says%20this%20with%20reference%20to%20Pakistan%2C%20relations%20with%20America%2C%20the%20G20%20and%20even%20International%20Yoga%20Day.%20Does%20the%20world%20perceive%20India%20as%20Modi%20sees%20it%3F%20As%20a%20vishwaguru%3F%20Or%20are%20there%20also%20deep%20concerns%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20diminishing%20democracy%2C%20increasing%20communalism%20and%20growing%20intolerance%20of%20dissent%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E11.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20talk%20about%20Modi%20the%20person.%20He%20is%20an%20incomparable%20orator.%20He%20has%20indefatigable%20energy%20and%20he%20is%20hugely%20popular.%20How%20does%20his%20personality%20compare%20with%20earlier%20prime%20ministers%20like%20Nehru%20and%20Indira%20Gandhi%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E12.%3C%2Fb%3E%20%3Cspan%3EModi%20is%20constantly%20targeting%20and%20belittling%20Nehru.%20Do%20you%20suspect%20he%20has%20a%20complex%20about%20him%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E13.%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20like%20critics%2C%20whether%20they%20are%20politicians%20or%20journalists.%20He%20uses%20terror%20and%20money%20laundering%20laws%20against%20them.%20He%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20hold%20press%20conferences.%20He%20only%20gives%20interviews%20to%20anchors%20who%20will%20never%20challenge%20him.%20What%20does%20this%20tell%20us%20of%20his%20political%20personality%3F%20Does%20it%20hint%20at%20a%20certain%20insecurity%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E14.%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20we%20end%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20talk%20a%20little%20about%20how%20India%20has%20changed%20under%20Modi.%20When%20I%20was%20young%2C%20no%20one%20accused%20Muslims%20of%20love%20jihad%20or%20cow%20lynching%2C%20no%20one%20called%20them%20Babar%20ki%20aulad%20and%20%3Cem%3Eabba%20jaan%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Now%20it%E2%80%99s%20commonplace.%20Has%20Modi%20awoken%20sleeping%20demons%20and%20made%20the%20unacceptable%20acceptable%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E15.%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3ELet%20me%20ask%20a%20deeper%20question.%20What%20has%20Modi%20revealed%20about%20Indians%3F%20Do%20we%20prefer%20authoritarian%20to%20democratic%20rulers%3F%20Are%20we%20prejudiced%20against%20Muslims%20and%20Islam%3F%20Are%20we%20taken%20in%20by%20his%20oratory%20and%20his%20event%20management%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E16.%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20Modi%20wins%20a%20third%20term%2C%20what%20do%20you%20anticipate%20and%20expect%3F%20Do%20you%20envisage%20or%2C%20perhaps%2C%20fear%20a%20push%20towards%20Hindu%20rashtra%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E17.%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3EFinally%2C%20what%20happens%20after%20Modi%3F%20He%E2%80%99ll%20be%2074%20this%20year%20and%20this%2C%20presumably%2C%20could%20be%20his%20last%20term.%20What%20will%20happen%20to%20the%20BJP%20after%20Modi%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709051428000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploa