0team%20against%20Route%20Mobile%20Limited%20in%20Navi%20Mumbai.%C2%A0Kishan%20kept%20the%20wickets%20for%20RBI%20as%20his%20team%20fielded%20first%20following%20Route%20Mobile's%20decision%20to%20bat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22zxx%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F4NVlYFIV60%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F4NVlYFIV60%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20World%20Cricket%20Live%20(%40world_cric_live)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fworld_cric_live%2Fstatus%2F1762461284216476074%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2027%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20return%2C%20Kishan%20played%20a%20part%20in%20one%20dismissal%20as%20he%20stumped%20Sumit%20Dhekale%20off%20Sayan%20Mondal%20at%20the%20DY%20Patil%20University%20Ground.%20Then%20with%20the%20bat%2C%20he%20entertained%20for%20a%20bit%20as%20he%20made%2019%20off%2012%20balls%20with%20two%20boundaries%20and%20a%20six.%C2%A0Kishan%20was%20dismissed%20while%20trying%20to%20hit%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Maxwell%20Swaminathan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F115389-maxwell-swaminathan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMaxwell%20Swaminathan%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20mid-off.%20RBI%20were%20chasing%20a%20target%20of%20193%20and%20Ishan%20Kishan%20fell%20in%C2%A0%20the%20fourth%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoute%20batted%20first%20and%20posted%20192%20for%20eight%20in%20their%2020%20overs%20thanks%20to%20Aayush%20Vartan's%2054%20off%2031%20balls%20with%20five%20boundaries%20and%20three%20sixes.%20Dhekale%20made%2042%20off%20just%2017%20balls%20with%20one%20boundary%20and%20five%20sixes.%20In%20their%20response%20RBI%20self-destructed%20as%20they%20were%20shot%20out%20for%20just%20103%20in%2016.3%20overs.%20For%20Route%20the%20best%20bowler%20was%20Badrey%20Alam%20(5-20).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20BCCI%20Secretary%20Jay%20Shah%20made%20it%20clear%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20all%20centrally%20contracted%20cricketers%20will%20have%20to%20mandatorily%20play%20red-ball%20cricket%20in%20the%20domestic%20circuit%20and%20the%20management%20will%20not%20tolerate%20any%20kind%20of%20excuses%20in%20the%20matter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20interacting%20with%20the%20reporters%20at%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20renaming%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Saurashtra%20Cricket%20Association%20Stadium%2C%20Shah%20pointed%20out%20that%20all%20players%20will%20have%20to%20represent%20their%20state%20teams%20if%20called%20upon%20by%20coach%20or%20captain.%20The%20statement%20came%20amidst%20the%20controversy%20surrounding%20Ishan%20Kishan%20and%20reports%20that%20suggest%20that%20BCCI%20has%20asked%20him%20to%20play%20for%20Jharkhand%20in%20Ranji%20Trophy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20mentioned%20Kishan%20during%20the%20interaction%20but%20quickly%20added%20that%20the%20announcement%20was%20not%20targeted%20towards%20him%20and%20this%20rule%20will%20apply%20for%20all%20cricketers%20who%20are%20not%20part%20of%20the%20national%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20contracted%20players%20have%20been%20told%20on%20phone%20and%20I'll%20be%20writing%20to%20them%20too.%20If%20chairman%20of%20selectors%2C%20coach%20%26amp%3B%20captain%20want%20you%20to%20play%20red-ball%20cricket%20then%20you%20gotta%20play.%20'Nakhre%20Nahi%20Chalenge'%20(no%20tantrums).%20And%20as%20far%20as%20Ishan%20Kishan%20is%20concerned%2C%20he%20is%20young%2C%20I%20am%20not%20saying%20this%20specifically%20about%20him%20as%20it%20will%20be%20applicable%20for%20all%20the%20players%20uniformly%2C%26quot%3B%20Jay%20Shah%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20will%20have%20to%20play%2C%20otherwise%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20selection%20committee%20has%20given%20me%20his%20suggestions%20and%20I%20am%20going%20to%20give%20him%20a%20free%20hand%20to%20let%20him%20take%20his%20own%20calls%20freely%2C%26quot%3B%2