accused%20of%20being%20partisan%20and%20acting%20on%20Mamata%20%5BBanerjee%5D%E2%80%99s%20instructions.%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20the%20BJP%20that%20the%20advocate%20general%20has%20informed%20the%20court%20that%2020%20arrests%20have%20been%20made%20in%20Sandeshkhali%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dev.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CThose%20who%20are%20accusing%20the%20West%20Bengal%20police%20of%20being%20partisan%2C%20we%20want%20to%20ask%20them%2C%20who%20is%20Shibu%20Hazra%3F%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20proved%20that%20whether%20it%20is%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20mothers%2C%20sisters%20or%20elderly%2C%20if%20there%20is%20any%20injustice%2C%20she%20will%20take%20action%20and%20not%20look%20at%20any%20party%20affiliation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHazra%2C%20a%20TMC%20block-level%20president%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20North%2024%20Parganas%20zilla%20parishad%2C%20was%20named%20by%20multiple%20women%20in%20serious%20sexual%20harassment%20cases%20and%20was%20only%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fsandeshkhali-unrest-as-women-led-protests-escalate-tmcs-outsider-claims-find-little-resonance%5C%22%3Earrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20earlier%20this%20month%20after%20the%20state%20government%20faced%20pressure%20from%20the%20opposition%2C%20including%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20a%20question%20by%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fi%3Eon%20why%20the%20state%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20act%20against%20Shahjahan%20despite%20allegations%20of%20land-grab%20and%20attacks%20on%20women%20being%20raised%20in%20the%20West%20Bengal%20assembly%20as%20far%20back%20as%20in%202012%2C%20the%20TMC%20leaders%20said%20that%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20had%20not%20been%20filed%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPolice%20file%20a%20complaint%20if%20there%20is%20an%20FIR.%20Tomorrow%2C%20I%20can%20stand%20and%20say%20something%20in%20front%20of%20the%20chief%20justice%20of%20India%2C%20but%20the%20police%20will%20investigate%20only%20when%20an%20FIR%20is%20filed%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Gokhale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20by%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fi%3Eabout%20why%20the%20issue%20being%20raised%20in%20the%20assembly%20did%20not%20warrant%20any%20action%2C%20Ghose%20added%20that%20now%20that%20FIRs%20have%20been%20registered%2C%20the%20police%20investigation%20has%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20that%20FIRs%20have%20come%2C%20the%20police%20are%20investigating%20and%20arresting%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%3Ci%3E%20The%20Telegraph%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fwest-bengal%2Fsandeshkhali-alert-in-records-former-cpm-mla-nirapada-sardar-took-up-atrocities-10-years-ago-in-house%2Fcid%2F2002964%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20citing%20official%20assembly%20records%20that%20CPI(M)%20MLA%20Nirapada%20Sardar%2C%20who%20represented%20Sandeshkhali%20from%202011%20to%202016%2C%20had%20raised%20those%20issues%20at%20least%20thrice%20%E2%80%93%20twice%20in%202012%20and%20once%20in%202013%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESardar%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20on%20February%2011%20on%20charges%20of%20fomenting%20trouble%20in%20Sandeshkhali%2C%20was%20granted%20bail%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20is%20proactively%20engaging%20on%20women%E2%80%99s%20issues%20across%20the%20state.%20In%20every%20area%2C%20the%20TMC%20government%20is%20looking%20to%20address%20grievances%20that%20are%20brought%20by%20the%20women%20of%20the%20area%20and%20when%20the%20complaint%20was%20registered%2C%20the%20government%20did%20act%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ghose%20to%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGokhale%20said%20that%20the%20state%20government%20had%20not%20acted%20against%20Shahjahan%20due%20to%20a%20February%207%20order%20by%20the%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20restraining%20