anted%20to%20build%20a%20solution%20that%20is%20good%20for%20the%20farmer%20as%20well%20as%20the%20planet%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rahul%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPrecision%20laser%20technology%20to%20kill%20weeds%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Frakshak1-min-1709042611.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rakshak%20is%20an%20AI-powered%20laser-weeding%20implement%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Frakshak1-min-1709042611.jpeg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Frakshak1-min-1709042611-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Frakshak1-min-1709042611-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Frakshak1-min-1709042611-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Frakshak1-min-1709042611-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Frakshak1-min-1709042611-150x200.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343339%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERakshak%20is%20an%20AI-powered%20laser-weeding%20implement%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20%E2%80%94%20who%20is%20now%20in%20the%20final%20year%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329484%2Fbengaluru-engineer-innovates-artificial-intelligence-powered-robot-sprayers-that-reduce-pesticides-costs-for-farmers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomputer%20science%20engineering%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20participated%20in%20many%20robotics%20competitions%20along%20with%20his%20friends%2C%20including%20the%20World%20Robotics%20Olympiad.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20building%20farming%20robots%20and%20realised%20that%20weeds%20are%20a%20huge%20problem.%20During%20internships%20at%20companies%20like%20FarmBot%2C%20we%20developed%20laser-based%20weed%20elimination%20solutions%20as%20proof%20of%20concept.%20Through%20this%20experience%2C%20I%20identified%20a%20gap%20in%20the%20Indian%20market%20for%20a%20laser%20weeder%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rahul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20using%20chemicals%20or%20hiring%20manual%20labour%2C%20Rahul%20decided%20to%20build%20laser%20technology%20for%20weed%20management.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhat%20started%20as%20a%20brainstorming%20session%20in%20December%202022%20evolved%20into%20a%20concrete%20vision%20within%20a%20few%20months.%20Through%20his%20university%E2%80%99s%20incubation%20programme%2C%20he%20received%20an%20initial%20funding%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeaming%20up%20with%20three%20friends%2C%20also%20final-year%20engineering%20students%20from%20different%20disciplines%20like%20mechanical%20and%20electronics%2C%20they%20embarked%20on%20developing%20a%20laser%20technology%20to%20combat%20weeds%20in%20June%202023.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOver%20the%20past%208%20months%2C%20they%20have%20received%20a%20total%20investment%20of%20Rs%2018%20lakh%20from%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20incubation%20centre%20to%20further%20develop%20this%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERakshak%20is%20a%20tractor-mounted%20laser%20weeder%20built%20using%20robotic%20platforms%20that%20utilise%20precision%20laser%20technology%20for%20weed%20eradication%2C%20which%20is%20paired%20with%20individual%20weed%20recognition%20through%20deep%20learning%20algorithms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20are%20some%20players%20globally%20who%20have%20built%20similar%20solutions%2C%20what%20differentiates%20Harvested%20Robotics%20is%20the%20power%20source%20of%20the%20laser%2C%20explains%20Rahul.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20burn%20weeds%20in%20India%2C%20you%20have%20to%20use%20at%20least%20200%20watts%20of%20laser%20source%20to%20burn%20it%20quickly.%20The%20global%20players%20use%20a%201%2C200-watt%20laser%2C%20which%20costs%20them%20%2440%2C000%20just%20for%20the%20laser%20%E2%80%94%20a%20restrictive%20cost.%20These%20lasers%20also%20have%20a%20very%20high%20maintenance%20cost%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2022-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20solve%20this%20problem%2C%20instead%20of%20relying%20on%20one%20big%20power%20source%2C%20Rahul%20and%20the%20team%20used%20a%20bunch%20of%20smaller%20laser%20sources%2C%20which%20they%20combined%20to%20get%20the%20same%20result.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20used%20five%20different%20laser%20sources%20to%20get%20200%20watts%20on%20the%20ground.%20This%20way%2C%20we%20were%20able%20to%20significantly%20reduce%20the%20cost%2C%20while%20ensuring%20even%20power%20distribution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20it%20works%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fembed%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3AugcPost%3A7148330471074975744%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Embedded%20post%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22584%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERakshak%20eliminates%20weeds%20down%20to%20their%20roots.%20It%20autonomously%20identifies%20weeds%20using%20cameras%20and%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20utilising%20blue%20laser%20technology%20for%20detection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20you%20drive%20the%20tractor%2C%20the%20machine%20uses%20computer%20vision%20and%20AI%20to%20detect%20what%E2%80%99s%20a%20weed%20and%20what%E2%80%99s%20not.%20Using%20precision%20technology%20and%20accuracy%2C%20the%20lasers%20burn%20them%20down.%20This%20also%20reduces%20the%20chances%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336695%2Finnovations-by-farmers-indian-agriculture-solar-dryer-biofertiliser-tree-scooter-organic-farming%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eregrowth%20of%20weeds%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20system%20is%20powered%20by%20the%20tractor%20battery%20itself%20and%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20need%20any%20external%20source%20for%20charging.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20depend%20on%20the%20horsepower%20of%20the%20tractor.%20All%20tractors%20have%20a%20three-point%20linkage%20where%20our%20implement%20gets%20attached.%20It%20is%20powered%20through%20the%20PTO%20(power%20take-off)%20or%20trolley%20trailer%20socket%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20robotic%20implement%20works%20on%20almost%20any%20tractor%2C%20across%20sizes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20this%20method%20is%20also%20a%20zero-chemical%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-27-at-10.44.22-1709043320.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20device%20can%20be%20easily%20attached%20to%20any%20tractor%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-27-at-10.44.22-1709043320.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-27-at-10.44.22-1709043320-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-27-at-10.44.22-1709043320-500x281.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-27-at-10.44.22-1709043320-768x432.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-27-at-10.44.22-1709043320-150x84.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343356%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20device%20can%20be%20easily%20attached%20to%20any%20tractor%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20using%20chemicals%20and%20not%20disturbing%20the%20soil.%20It%20preserves%20the%20soil%20and%20maintains%20the%20crop%E2%80%99s%20integrity%20as%20tilling%20methods%20are%20not%20used.%20We%20concentrate%20the%20laser%20on%20the%20stem%20point%20of%20the%20weed%2C%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20destroying%20the%20water%20cells%20inside%20the%20plant%2C%20so%20that%20the%20water-absorbing%20capacity%20is%20lost%20and%20the%20plant%20dies.%20The%20leaves%20eventually%20fall%20out%20and%20will%20become%20manure%20for%20other%20crops%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Rahul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20weeds%20tend%20to%20grow%20again%20in%20other%20methods%20of%20weed%20management%2C%20this%20is%20more%20sustainable%2C%20he%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLaser%20weeder%20machines%20in%20the%20US%20cost%20a%20million%20dollars.%20Our%20solution%20is%20the%20most%20affordable%20in%20the%20world.%20It%20will%20also%20reduce%20the%20number%20of%20weeding%20cycles%20and%20time.%20Such%20technology%20is%20not%20available%20in%20India%20and%20we%20have%20also%20applied%20for%20a%20patent%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20other%20available%20machines%20use%20carbon%20dioxide-based%20technology%2C%20are%20huge%2C%20and%20have%20a%20high%20maintenance%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COther%20solutions%20use%20invisible%20laser%20technology%20while%20we%20use%20blue%20laser%20light%20which%20penetrates%20faster%20through%20chlorophyll%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20and%20his%20team%20built%20the%20implement%20over%20eight%20months%20and%20have%20conducted%20trials%20in%20farms%20across%20India.%20Harvested%20Robotics%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Microsoft%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343156%2Ftoxin-free-home-cleaning-products-delhi-simran-khara-koparo-startup-shark-tank-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStartups%20Founders%20Hub%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20they%20are%20also%20working%20with%20Mahindra%20%26amp%3B%20Mahindra%20to%20test%20their%20product.%20They%20are%20gearing%20up%20to%20launch%20their%20product%20in%20the%20market%20in%20the%20next%20few%20months%2C%20and%20it%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20priced%20at%20Rs%2010%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20more%20information%2C%20you%20can%20contact%20Rahul%20at%20rahul.arepaka%40gmail.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709043839000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D343321%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Founder%20of%20Harvested%20Robotics%2C%20Rahul%20Arepaka%20(22)%20built%20Rakshak%2C%20an%20AI-powered%20laser-weeding%20robot%20that%20combats%20weeds%20without%20harming%20the%20crops.%20He%20is%20now%20using%20it%20to%20help%20farmers%20earn%20more.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343321%2Frahul-arepaka-harvested-robotics-hyderabad-ai-startup-laser-weeder-robot-help-farmers-earn-more%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bihar%20Caste%20Survey%3A%20The%20Who%E2%80%99s%20Who%20in%20the%20Data%20%7C%20Naalband%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27194430%2FHorseshoe-Flickr-e1709043300940.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBeyond%20politics%2C%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%20is%20a%20revolutionary%20document.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20public%20document%2C%20the%20first%20ever%20after%201931%2C%20allowing%20for%20people%20to%20stand%20up%20and%20be%20counted.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20go%20down%20to%20the%20wire%2C%20on%20what%20each%20of%20the%20numbers%20unveiled%20mean.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWho%20are%20the%20people%20referred%20to%20by%20percentages%20in%20the%20survey%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EToday%20we%20look%20at%20Naalband%20(11%2C900)%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Islam%20is%20in%20many%20ways%20different%20from%20Hinduism%2C%20many%20of%20its%20the%20followers%20in%20India%20are%20divided%20into%20various%20castes%20and%20families%20and%20few%20traverse%20these%20boundaries%20to%20form%20matrimonial%20alliances%20in%20a%20mark%20of%20similarity%20between%20the%20two%20religions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20one%20compares%20these%20categories%20with%20the%20castes%20that%20exist%20in%20the%20Hindu%20religion%2C%20one%20can%20say%20that%20they%20are%20similarly%20mapped%20as%20the%20S%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eavarnas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20S%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehudras%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20those%20who%20were%20and%20are%20considered%20the%20%E2%80%98untouchables%E2%80%99%20in%20India.%20However%2C%20the%20Bihar%20government%20has%20defined%20them%20as%20upper%20castes%2C%20backward%20classes%20and%20extremely%20backward%20classes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20273px)%2085vw%2C%20273px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-715x1024.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22273%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-715x1024.jpg%20715w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-210x300.jpg%20210w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%20838w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22391%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20caste-based%20census%20report%20released%20by%20the%20Bihar%20government%2C%20out%20of%20the%20total%20population%20of%20the%20state%20(130%2C725%2C310)%20the%20Muslim%20population%20is%2023%2C149%2C925%2C%20or%2017.7%25.%20Among%20them%2C%20the%20population%20of%20elite%20class%20Muslims%20(Sheikh%2C%20Pathan%20and%20Syed)%20is%206%2C280%2C537.%20Although%2C%20traditionally%20Mughals%20are%20also%20included%20among%20the%20privileged%20classes%2C%20in%20the%20report%20of%20Bihar%20government%2C%20they%20have%20been%20categorised%20as%20%E2%80%98Others%E2%80%99.%20According%20to%20an%20estimate%2C%20their%20population%20in%20the%20Mithila%20region%2C%20including%20Darbhanga%20and%20Madhubani%20is%20around%2010%2C000%20to%2015%2C000.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20latter%20half%20of%20the%201990s%2C%20Bihar%20witnessed%20a%20new%20kind%20of%20movement%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Pasmanda%20Movement.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EPasmanda%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20a%20Persian%20word%20which%20means%20%E2%80%98one%20who%20is%20left%20behind%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20is%20now%20used%20to%20describe%20those%20who%20have%20been%20neglected%20or%20suppressed.%20There%20has%20long%20been%20a%20struggle%20in%20the%20downtrodden%20section%20of%20the%20Muslim%20society%20regarding%20its%20identity%20and%20rights.%20But%20it%20took%20a%20new%20form%20in%20the%20latter%20half%20of%20the%20nineties%2C%20when%20Ali%20Anwar%20openly%20used%20this%20word%20with%20its%20political%20connotations%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAli%20Anwar%20was%20made%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20twice%20by%20the%20ruling%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20in%20Bihar.%20A%20journalist%20by%20profession%2C%20Anwar%2C%20tried%20to%20establish%20unity%20between%20the%20backward%20and%20extra%20backward%20classes%20through%20the%20Pasmanda%20movement.%20However%2C%20this%20movement%20was%20one%20to%20create%20a%20divide%20in%20the%20Muslim%20community%20of%20the%20state%20and%20its%20political%20impact%20was%20such%20that%20the%20JD(U)%20successfully%20made%20a%20dent%20in%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20Muslim%20vote%20bank.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Pasmanda%20movement%20is%20still%20a%20vocal%20movement.%20It%20has%20brought%20the%20Muslims%20in%20backward%20and%20extra%20backward%20classes%20closer%20to%20each%20other%20in%20the%20society.%20Together%2C%20the%20total%20population%20of%20Pasmanda%20Muslims%20(who%20are%20included%20in%20the%20backward%20class%20and%20extremely%20backward%20class)%20is%2016%2C869%2C388.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20also%20worth%20noting%20that%20most%20of%20the%20Pasmanda%20castes%20are%20included%20in%20the%20extremely%20backward%20classes.%20The%20share%20of%20Pasmanda%20Muslims%20included%20in%20the%20backward%20class%20in%20the%20total%20population%20of%20Bihar%20is%20only%202.1124%25%20and%20the%20castes%20included%20are%20%E2%80%93%20Surjapuri%20Muslim%2C%20Malik%2C%20Naalband%2C%20Kagzi%2C%20Gaddi%2C%20Sukiaar%20and%20Rautiya.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20discuss%20the%20Naalband%20caste.%20This%20caste%20group%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20the%20farming%20communities%20of%20the%20country.%20The%20members%20of%20this%20caste%20group%20fix%20shoes%20in%20the%20hooves%20of%20horses%20and%20oxen.%20When%20bulls%20and%20horses%20were%20used%20as%20a%20means%20of%20transportation%2C%20people%20of%20the%20Naalband%20caste%20used%20to%20roam%20from%20village%20to%20village%20carrying%20iron%20shoes%20for%20horses%20and%20oxen%2C%20hammer%20and%20nails.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20method%20of%20shoeing%20is%20quite%20painful%20for%20the%20animal.%20First%2C%20the%20bull%20or%20horse%20is%20overpowered%20by%20pushing%20it%20on%20the%20ground%20with%20the%20help%20of%20ropes.%20The%20farrier%20then%20removes%20the%20old%20shoe%20fixed%20in%20the%20hooves.%20Then%20the%20hooves%20are%20cleaned%20and%20flattened%2C%20sometimes%20with%20an%20iron%20sander%2C%20so%20that%20the%20shoe%20can%20fit%20easily.%20After%20this%20a%20new%20shoe%20is%20inserted.%20Generally%2C%20only%20the%20bulls%20used%20in%20bullock%20carts%20are%20shoed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApart%20from%20shoeing%20animals%2C%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Naalband%20caste%20group%20also%20used%20to%20castrate%20calves%20to%20convert%20them%20into%20bulls.%20Among%20Hindus%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Nat%20caste%20also%20perform%20this%20task%20but%20Naalband%20folk%20are%20considered%20masters%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20this%20job.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20caste%20group%20is%20included%20in%20the%20backward%20class%20in%20Bihar%20and%20its%20total%20population%20is%20only%2011%2C900.%20The%20government%20report%20itself%20shows%20that%20out%20of%20a%20total%20of%202%2C461%20families%2C%20803%20are%20poor.%20Here%20poor%20means%20those%20whose%20daily%20income%20is%20limited%20to%20Rs%20200.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20time%2C%20the%20use%20of%20horses%20and%20bulls%20have%20declined.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20traditional%20work%20of%20the%20Naalband%20caste%20members%20ended%20and%20they%20took%20up%20other%20professions.%20However%2C%20even%20now%20in%20rural%20areas%20where%20bullock%20carts%20and%20chariots%20are%20still%20in%20use%2C%20Naalband%20can%20be%20seen%20shoeing%20animals.%20But%20they%20are%20very%20few%20in%20number.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20how%20human%20civilisation%20has%20evolved.%20First%2C%20professions%20were%20formed%20and%20then%20castes%20were%20created%20out%20of%20these%20professions.%20Now%2C%20traditional%20professions%20are%20dying%20out%2C%20but%20caste%20remains%20the%20same.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Hindi%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%20Read%20the%20Hindi%20original%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F263541%2Fbihar-caste-survey-naalband-community-society%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20earlier%20parts%20of%20the%20series%20on%20the%20following%20communities%20by%20clicking%20on%20their%20names%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-ghasi%5C%22%3EGhasi%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3ESantrash%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-santrash%5C%22%3EMadaria%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-koeri-kushwaha%5C%22%3EKoeri%2FKushwaha%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-chaupal%5C%22%3EChaupal%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-nai-hajjaam%5C%22%3ENai%2FHajjaam%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-pasi%5C%22%3EPasi%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-rangrez%5C%22%3ERangrez%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-chamar%5C%22%3EChamar%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-gorka