%C2%A0said%20that%20%E2%80%9Caid%20was%20supposed%20to%20increase%20not%20decrease%E2%80%9D%C2%A0to%20meet%20the%20huge%20needs%20of%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20two%20million%20people%2C%20who%20are%20living%20in%20desperate%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20listed%20some%20of%20the%20obstacles%20to%20aid%20delivery%2C%20including%20lack%20of%20political%20will%2C%20the%20regular%20closing%20of%20the%20two%20crossing%20points%20into%20the%20enclave%2C%20as%20well%20as%20insecurity%20due%20to%20military%20operations%20and%20the%20collapse%20of%20civil%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20a%20ceasefire%2C%20along%20with%20%E2%80%9Clifting%20the%20siege%20to%20allow%20meaningful%20lifesaving%20aid%20and%20commercial%20supplies%2C%20are%20long%20overdue%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESecurity%20concerns%20and%20crossing%20closures%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20average%2C%20nearly%2098%20aid%20trucks%20entered%20Gaza%20this%20month%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unrwa.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUNRWA%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0said%20in%20its%20latest%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unrwa.org%2Fresources%2Freports%2Funrwa-situation-report-82-situation-gaza-strip-and-west-bank-including-east-Jerusalem%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esituation%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20issued%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20noted%20%E2%80%9Csignificant%20difficulties%E2%80%9D%20in%20bringing%20supplies%20through%20the%20Kerem%20Shalom%20and%20Rafah%20crossings%20due%20to%20security%20constraints%20and%20temporary%20closures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUNRWA%20has%20at%20times%20had%20to%20temporarily%20stop%20discharging%20supplies%20due%20to%20security%20concerns.%C2%A0Security%20to%20manage%20the%20crossing%20has%20been%20severely%20impacted%20due%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20several%20Palestinian%20policemen%20in%20Israeli%20airstrikes%C2%A0near%20the%20crossings%20recently%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInflux%20and%20airstrikes%20in%20Rafah%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGround%20operations%20and%20heavy%20fighting%20continue%20across%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20particularly%20in%20northern%20Gaza%2C%20Deir%20al%20Balah%20and%20Khan%20Younis%2C%20the%20agency%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20fleeing%20intense%20fighting%20in%20and%20around%20Khan%20Younis%20continue%20to%20head%20further%20south%20to%20overcrowded%20Rafah.%20Some%201.5%20million%20Palestinians%20are%20sheltering%20in%20the%20city%2C%20which%20remains%20a%20focus%20of%20international%20concern%20amid%20the%20threat%20of%20an%20all-out%20Israeli%20offensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIncreased%20airstrikes%20in%20Rafah%2C%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3Eincluding%20in%20residential%20areas%20without%20prior%20warnings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0have%20heightened%20fears%20that%20they%20will%20further%20hamper%20overstretched%20humanitarian%20operations%2C%E2%80%9D%20UNRWA%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20people%20have%20been%20moving%20out%20of%20Rafah%20towards%20Deir%20Al%20Balah%20and%20Nuseirat%20refugee%20camps%20in%20the%20Middle%20Area%20of%20Gaza%2C%20even%20though%20there%20are%20reports%20of%20further%20fighting%20and%20airstrikes%20in%20those%20locations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHumanitarian%20update%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2075%25%20of%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20up%20to%201.7%20million%20people%2C%20have%20been%20displaced%20since%20the%20start%20of%20hostilities%20following%20the%20brutal%20Hamas-led%20terrorist%20attacks%20in%20Israel%20on%207%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUN%20agencies%20continue%20to%20warn%20of%20the%20deepening%20hunger%20crisis%20in%20Gaza.%20More%20than%20two%20million%20people%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ochaopt.org%2Fcontent%2Fhostilities-g