%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20do%20more%2C%20we%20need%20safe%20and%20unimpeded%20routes%20in%20Gaza.%20We%20also%20need%20more%20trucks%20and%20fuel%20inside%20Gaza%20to%20ensure%20a%20consistent%20and%20dependable%20food%20supply%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20agency%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrime%20Minister%20resigns%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUN%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fsg%2F%5C%22%3ESecretary-General%20Ant%C3%B3nio%20Guterres%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0has%20taken%20note%20of%20the%20resignation%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20Government%2C%20his%20Spokesperson%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.un.org%2Fsg%2Fen%2Fcontent%2Fossg%2Fnoon-briefing-highlight%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Mohammad%20Shtayyeh%20submitted%20the%20resignation%20in%20writing%20to%20Palestinian%20President%20Mahmoud%20Abbas%20earlier%20that%20day%2C%20according%20to%20media%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20United%20Nations%20stands%20ready%20to%20continue%20supporting%20efforts%20aimed%20at%20overcoming%20the%20humanitarian%2C%20political%2C%20financial%20as%20well%20as%20security%20challenges%20facing%20the%20Palestinian%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20UN%20Spokesperson%20St%C3%A9phane%20Dujarric%20told%20journalists%20attending%20his%20regular%20press%20briefing%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20%E2%80%9Ca%20strengthened%2C%20empowered%20Palestinian%20Government%2C%20that%20can%20administer%20the%20whole%20of%20the%20occupied%20Palestinian%20Territory%2C%20is%20critical%20as%20part%20of%20a%20path%20to%20achieving%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20fully%20independent%2C%20democratic%2C%20contiguous%2C%20sovereign%20and%20viable%20Palestinian%20State%2C%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%201967%20lines%2C%20of%20which%20Gaza%20is%20an%20integral%20part%2C%20which%20remains%20the%20only%20way%20to%20achieve%20a%20lasting%20peace.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3