dia.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkavi-12-1709039014-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-343310%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHaleem%20%E2%80%93%20a%20must-try%20dish%20of%20Hyderabad.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E8.%20Pathar%20ka%20Gosht%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20are%20in%20Hyderabad%20and%20have%20not%20tried%20the%20delicious%20Pathar%20Ka%20Gosht%2C%20your%20trip%20is%20incomplete.%20Pathar%20ka%20Gosht%2C%20which%20translates%20to%20%E2%80%9CMeat%20cooked%20on%20stone%E2%80%9D%2C%20is%20prepared%20by%20cooking%20marinated%20meat%20on%20a%20hot%20stone%2C%20infusing%20it%20with%20a%20unique%20smoky%20flavour%20and%20tender%20texture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20meat%20cooks%20on%20the%20hot%20stone%2C%20it%20absorbs%20the%20heat%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20seared%20exterior%20and%20a%20juicy%2C%20succulent%20interior.%20If%20you%20are%20looking%20for%20the%20perfect%20place%20to%20try%20them%2C%20then%20Bade%20Miyan%20Kabab%20is%20the%20answer.%20According%20to%20a%20News18%20article%2C%20the%20place%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20in%20Hyderabad%20and%20%E2%80%9Cthey%20(the%20restaurant)%20have%20been%20following%20the%20recipe%20since%201954%2C%20encompassing%20two%20generations.%20The%20tradition%20of%20making%20Patthar%20Ka%20Gosht%20is%20said%20to%20date%20way%20back%20to%20the%20Nizam%20era.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkavi-13-1709039050.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pathar%20Ka%20Gosht%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkavi-13-1709039050.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2