8Are%20you%20sure%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20anxiety%3F'%E2%80%9D%20one%20woman%20in%20her%20late%2050s%20told%20researchers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20never%20suffered%20from%20anxiety%2C%20and%20I%20still%20don%E2%80%99t.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20woman%2C%20aged%2050%2C%20found%20doctor%20appointments%20to%20be%20invalidating%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20doctors%20cannot%20help%20you.%20They%20actually%20make%20you%20worse%20because%20they%20make%20your%20stress%20worse%20by%20saying%20it%E2%80%99s%20in%20your%20head.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Feurope%2Fnews-room%2Ffact-sheets%2Fitem%2Fpost-covid-19-condition%5C%22%3ELong%20COVID%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0usually%20develops%20three%20months%20after%20the%20initial%20infection.%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41467-022-29521-z%5C%22%3ESymptoms%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0such%20as%20fatigue%2C%20shortness%20of%20breath%2C%20cognitive%20dysfunction%20and%20around%20200%20others%2C%20last%20at%20least%20two%20months.%20There%20are%20no%20specific%20treatments%20or%20vaccines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUp%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Feurope%2Fnews-room%2Ffact-sheets%2Fitem%2Fpost-covid-19-condition%5C%22%3E20%25%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20people%20infected%20with%20COVID-19%20may%20develop%20long%20COVID.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhpr.termedia.pl%2FThe-hidden-pandemic-a-qualitative-study-on-how-middle-aged-women-make-sense-of-managing%2C169811%2C0%2C2.html%5C%22%3Eresearch%3C%2Fa%3E%20came%20about%20because%20there%20was%20a%20gap%20in%20knowledge%20of%20how%20women%20who%20developed%20long%20COVID%20during%20the%20first%20wave%20of%20COVID%20%E2%80%93%20from%20March%202020%20%E2%80%93%20were%20managing%20their%20symptoms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENine%20women%2C%20eight%20from%20England%20and%20one%20from%20Poland%2C%20discussed%20their%20medical%20care%2C%20which%20they%20reported%20as%20mostly%20being%20negative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMedical%20gaslighting%20is%20the%20process%20of%20diminishing%20or%20dismissing%20the%20physical%20or%20mental%20health%20symptoms%20of%20a%20patient%20by%20a%20healthcare%20provider.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20patient%20may%20be%20told%20their%20symptoms%20are%20in%20their%20head%20or%20given%20a%20vague%20explanation%20leaving%20them%20without%20a%20treatment%20plan%20or%20diagnosis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20women%20reported%20being%20mistreated%20when%20attempting%20to%20ask%20for%20medical%20support%20for%20their%20long%20COVID%20symptoms.%20They%20also%20felt%20their%20health%20concerns%20were%20not%20being%20prioritised%20or%20taken%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20woman%20who%20had%20attended%20a%20long%20COVID%20clinic%2C%20said%20she%20noticed%20sexist%2C%20ageist%20and%20discriminatory%20assumptions%20were%20made%20about%20her%20being%20a%20woman%20over%2040%20%E2%80%93%20with%20healthcare%20providers%20assuming%20her%20symptoms%20were%20due%20to%20menopause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHysteria%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20health%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20experience%20is%20an%20example%20of%20gaslighting%20%E2%80%93%20which%20can%20involve%20doctors%20telling%20a%20patient%20their%20symptoms%20are%20in%20their%20head%2C%20giving%20a%20vague%20explanation%20and%20leaving%20them%20without%20a%20treatment%20plan%20or%20diagnosis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaslighting%20can%20also%20lead%20to%20genuine%20symptoms%20and%20diagnoses%20being%20overlooked%20because%20medical%20staff%20dismiss%20women%20as%20emotional%2C%20dramatic%20and%20%E2%80%9Chysterical%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20long%20history%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20health%20care%20being%20classified%20as%20hysteria%20%E2%80%93%20although%20the%20diagnosis%20has%20now%20been%20replaced%20with%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flup.lub.lu.se%2Fluur%2Fdownload%3Ffunc%3DdownloadFile%26recordOId%3D9093406%26fileOId%3D9093410%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cmedically%20unexplained%20symptoms%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20label%20has%20been%20applied%20to%20unexplainable%20and%20chronic%20health%20conditions%20in%20women%E2%80%99s%20health%20care%20such%20as%20chronic%20fatigue%20syndrome%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bmj.com%2Fcontent%2F374%2Fbmj.n1859%5C%22%3Elong%20COVID%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.siena.edu%2Ffiles%2Fresources%2Fgleanings-2021-publication.pdf%23page%3D88%5C%22%3Eresearch%20papers%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0point%20to%20medical%20misogyny%20as%20they%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindawi.com%2Fjournals%2Fprm%2F2018%2F6358624%2F%5C%22%3Ehighlight%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0the%20many%20ways%20in%20which%20women%20who%20experience%20pain%20are%20often%20viewed%20by%20the%20medical%20establishment%20as%20hysterical%2C%20malingerers%2C%20not%20helping%20themselves%20to%20get%20better%20or%20fabricating%20the%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20woman%20in%20the%20study%20pointed%20to%20language%20used%20in%20scientific%20research%20as%20an%20example%20of%20these%20sexist%20assumptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20some%20people%20who%20are%20studying%20long%20COVID%2C%20usually%2C%20unfortunately%20from%20the%20psychological%20side%2C%20will%20start%20talking%20about%20things%20like%20neurasthenia%20or%20hysteria%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20woman%2C%20in%20her%20late%2040s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20very%20misogynist%20language.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EEliminating%20misogyny%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEliminating%20medical%20misogyny%20and%20medical%20gaslighting%20is%20no%20small%20feat%2C%20but%20there%20are%20some%20obvious%20places%20to%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.siena.edu%2Ffiles%2Fresources%2Fgleanings-2021-publication.pdf%23page%3D88%5C%22%3Emedical%20research%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20mostly%20based%20on%20male%20biology%20in%20clinical%20studies%2C%20researchers%20can%20play%20a%20key%20role%20by%20including%20more%20women%20in%20their%20studies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOffering%20mindfulness%20interventions%20may%20support%20women%20with%20long%20COVID.%20While%20not%20a%20cure%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC9653042%2F%5C%22%3Emindfulness%20can%20play%20a%20role%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cu%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fu%3Ein%20helping%20sufferers%20manage%20debilitating%20symptoms%20including%20fatigue%20and%20unrefreshing%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrucially%2C%20doctors%20can%20also%20commit%20to%20listening%20to%20female%20patients.%20Women%20know%20their%20own%20bodies%20and%20when%20something%20feels%20off.%20It%20can%20be%20empowering%20for%20a%20woman%20to%20trust%20their%20instinct%20and%20to%20advocate%20for%20their%20health%20and%20to%20ask%20for%20a%20second%20opinion%20when%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20research%20suggests%20all%20healthcare%20providers%20need%20to%20validate%20women%E2%80%99s%20health%20concerns%20when%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20access%20care%20for%20long%20COVID.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20would%20reduce%20discrimination%20and%20misogynistic%20practices%2C%20as%20well%20as%20helping%20women%20access%20the%20support%20they%20need.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EAdditional%20reporting%20and%20contributions%20by%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cem%3EDisa%20Collier%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ci%3E%2C%20a%20telephone%20and%20online%20counsellor%2C%20qualitative%20researcher%20with%20interests%20in%20long%20COVID%2C%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20mental%20health%20and%20chronic%20health%20conditions%2C%20and%20an%20alumnus%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Derby%E2%80%99s%20MSc%20Psychology%20programme.%20The%20research%20was%20conducted%20as%20part%20of%20Disa%E2%80%99s%20MSc%20psychology%20degree.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EG%C3%BClcan%20Garip%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%20is%20a%20Health%20and%20Care%20Professions%20Council%20registered%20health%20psychologist%2C%20chartered%20psychologist%20with%20the%20British%20Psychological%20Society%20and%20the%20programme%20co-lead%20for%20the%20MSc%20Psychology%20programme%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Derby.%20Garip%20is%20a%20senior%20fellow%20of%20the%20Higher%20Education%20Academy%20and%20supervised%20Disa%E2%80%99s%20MSc%20Psychology%20research%20project.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EOriginally%20published%20under%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcreativecommons.org%2Flicenses%2Fby%2F4.0%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3ECreative%20Commons%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%C2%A0by%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F360info.org%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E360info%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709041506000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27180657%2Fpexels-liza-summer-6382660.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fgaslighting-doctors-harder-women-long-covid%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gaslighting%20can%20lead%20to%20genuine%20symptoms%20and%20diagnoses%20being%20overlooked%20because%20medical%20staff%20dismiss%20women%20as%20emotional%2C%20dramatic%20and%20%26quot%3Bhysterical%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fgaslighting-doctors-harder-women-long-covid%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20ship%20sinking%20in%20Red%20Sea%20after%20Houthi%20attack%20drifts%20north%20-%20as%20US%20Navy%20offer%20help%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709041140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F1600x900%2Fskynews-rubymar-ship_6470981.png%3F20240227140357%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fuk-ship-sinking-in-red-sea-after-houthi-attack-drifts-north-as-us-navy-offer-help-13082231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20UK-registered%20Rubymar%20cargo%20vessel%20appears%20to%20be%20drifting%20nor