n-indian-carriers-at-present-says-airasia-124022700915_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fnot-looking-to-acquire-stake-in-indian-carriers-at-present-says-airasia-124022700915_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fnot-looking-to-acquire-stake-in-indian-carriers-at-present-says-airasia-124022700915_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Across%20Assam%2C%20Hindutva%20Group's%20Posters%20Issue%20'Final%20Warnings'%20to%20Christian%20Institutions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27181706%2FUntitled-design-2-6.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20%3Cspan%3EFollowing%20a%20recent%20call%20by%20a%20Hindutva%20group%2C%20Sanmilita%20Sanatan%20Samaj%2C%20to%20avoid%20all%20religious%20symbols%20and%20costumes%20in%20educational%20institutions%20in%20Assam%2C%20a%20number%20of%20top%20Christian%20institutions%20across%20the%20northeastern%20state%20have%20seen%20posters%20stuck%20on%20their%20premises%2C%20warning%20them%20against%20using%20their%20schools%20as%20religious%20institutions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20posters%2C%20printed%20by%20the%20group%20in%20Assamese%2C%20have%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20final%20warning%20to%20stop%20using%20the%20school%20as%20a%20religious%20institution%E2%80%A6stop%20anti-Bharat%20and%20unconstitutional%20activities%20or%20else%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20minority%20institutions%20were%20asked%20to%20%E2%80%9Cremove%E2%80%9D%20churches%20from%20within%20their%20school%20premises%2C%20along%20with%20all%20idols%20of%20Jesus%20and%20Mary.%20The%20posters%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CChristian%20missionary%20educational%20institutions%20should%20stop%20ignoring%20the%20proposed%20New%20Education%20Policy%20(of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government)%20and%20show%20respect%20to%20the%20Indian%20Parliament.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20February%2018%2C%20authorities%20at%20the%20well-known%20Carmel%20School%20in%20Jorhat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fnorth-east%2Fassam-christian-school-faces-statue-threat-seeks-police-protection%2Fcid%2F2001270%5C%22%3Eapproached%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20local%20police%20after%20spotting%20such%20a%20poster%20on%20its%20boundary%20wall.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20application%2C%20written%20by%20school%20principal%20Sister%20Rose%20Fatima%2C%20said%20that%20her%20institution%20had%20%E2%80%98been%20very%20accommodating%20and%20respectful%20towards%20people%20of%20every%20religion%20and%20culture%E2%80%99%20and%20maintained%20an%20%E2%80%98atmosphere%20of%20peace%20and%20tranquility%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20reported%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20news%20report%20said%20that%20the%20police%20station%20had%20confirmed%20the%20development%20and%20was%20investigating%20the%20matter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESoon%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthemeghalayan.com%2Fanother-hindu-radical-group-launches-poster-campaign-against-christian-schools-across-assam%2F%5C%22%3Eposters%20were%20spotted%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20Don%20Bosco%20Boys%20School%20and%20Saint%20Mary%E2%80%99s%20School%20in%20Guwahati%20and%20other%20Christian%20minority%20schools%20in%20Barpeta%2C%20Dibrugarh%20and%20Sivasagar%20towns.%20Posters%20were%20signed%20in%20Guwahati%E2%80%99s%20busy%20Dighalipukhuri%20area%20and%20Nehru%20Park%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20news%20reports%2C%20the%20poster%20campaign%20by%20the%20Guwahati-based%20outfit%20begun%20after%20it%20asked%20Christian%20missionary-run%20schools%20on%20February%207%20to%20remove%20all%20religious%20symbols%20and%20statues%20from%20their%20premises%20within%2015%20days.%20A%20similar%20diktat%20was%20issued%20by%20another%20group%2C%20Kutumba%20Suraksha%20Parishad%2C%20recently.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20against%20the%20Christians.%20But%20we%20are%20against%20the%20subtle%20use%20of%20religious%20symbols%20aimed%20at%20conversion.%20The%20missionary%20schools%20focus%20on%20propagating%20Christianity%2C%20not%20India%20or%20Indian%20culture%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Sanmilita%20Sanatan%20Samaj%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fassam-hindu-group-starts-poster-campaign-against-missionary-schools%2Farticle67881789.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%25E2%2580%259CWe%2520are%2520not%2520against%2520the%2Cmember%2520of%2520the%2520group%2520said%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Assam%20Christian%20Forum%20has%20termed%20these%20posters%20an%20act%20by%20%E2%80%9Cfringe%20elements%E2%80%9D%20but%20has%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20institutions%20have%20alerted%20the%20state%20director%20general%20of%20police%20and%20the%20relevant%20district%20police%20chiefs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20institutions%20have%20always%20respected%20and%20accommodated%20individuals%20of%20all%20religions%20and%20cultures%2C%20maintaining%20a%20peaceful%20and%20tranquil%20atmosphere.%20Had%20conversion%20been%20our%20goal%2C%20at%20least%20half%20of%20Assam%20would%20have%20been%20Christians%20by%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Forum%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20about%20400%20such%20educational%20institutions%20runs%20by%20Christian%20missionaries%20across%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHimanta%E2%80%99s%20comments%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20poster%20campaign%20by%20the%20Hindutva%20groups%20has%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Assam%20chief%20minister%20has%20equated%20magical%20healing%20with%20proselytisation%20by%20Christian%20missionaries.%20BJP%20government%20in%20Assam%20has%20tabled%20a%20controversial%20bill%20in%20the%20assembly.%20Named%20Assam%20(Healing)%20Prevention%20of%20Evil%20Practices%20Bill%2C%202024%2C%20the%20proposed%20law%20was%20tabled%20in%20the%20assembly%20on%20February%2021.%20CM%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%2C%20thereafter%2C%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20Bill%20would%20stop%20all%20healing%20practices%20which%20are%20carried%20out%20by%20some%20with%20an%20ulterior%20motive%20in%20the%20state%2C%20leading%20the%20Assam%20Christian%20Forum%20to%20call%20it%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmisguided%20and%20misleading%E2%80%9D%20comment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHealing%2C%20in%20our%20context%2C%20is%20not%20synonymous%20with%20proselytisation.%20It%20is%20a%20compassionate%20response%20to%20human%20suffering%2C%20irrespective%20of%20religious%20affiliations%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20forum%20said%2C%20insisting%20that%20labelling%20prayer%20as%20magical%20healing%20oversimplifies%20the%20profound%20spiritual%20dimensions%20of%20faith%20and%20life.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Bill%20has%20also%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnenews.in%2Fnagaland%2Fnagaland-baptist-church-council-denounces-assam-healing-bill-2024-as-insensitive%2F7438%2F%5C%22%3Ecriticised%20by%20Nagaland%20Baptist%20Church%20Council%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Council%20has%20termed%20it%20a%20manifestation%20of%20%E2%80%9Creligious%20bigotry%E2%80%9D%20and%20an%20%E2%80%9Cinsensitive%20act%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709039751000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27181706%2FUntitled-design-2-6.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhindutva-group-assam-christian-institutions%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20posters%2C%20printed%20by%20the%20Sammilata%20Sanatan%20Samaj%20group%20in%20Assamese%2C%20have%20said%2C%20'This%20is%20the%20final%20warning%20to%20stop%20using%20the%20school%20as%20a%20religious%20institution%E2%80%A6stop%20anti-Bharat%20and%20unconstitutional%20activities%20or%20else%E2%80%A6'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A24%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhindutva-group-assam-christian-institutions%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bihar%20Caste%20Survey%3A%20The%20Who%E2%80%99s%20Who%20in%20the%20Data%20%7C%20Kahar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27183834%2FPalanquin-Kahar-Pic-credit-NYPL1-e1709039448261.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBeyond%20politics%2C%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20survey%20is%20a%20revolutionary%20document.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20public%20document%2C%20the%20first%20ever%20after%201931%2C%20allowing%20for%20people%20to%20stand%20up%20and%20be%20counted.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20go%20down%20to%20the%20wire%2C%20on%20what%20each%20of%20the%20numbers%20unveiled%20mean.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWho%20are%20the%20people%20referred%20to%20by%20percentages%20in%20the%20survey%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EToday%20we%20look%20at%20Kahar%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E(2%2C155%2C644%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20caste%20group%20we%20are%20going%20to%20discuss%20today%20is%20Kahar.%20They%20are%20also%20known%20as%20Ramani%2C%20Rawani%20and%20Kamkar.%20Now%2C%20some%20people%20have%20also%20started%20referring%20to%20them%20as%20Chandravanshi.%20There%20are%20both%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20among%20Kahars.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20things%20changed%20as%20human%20civilization%20progressed.%20Thought%20processes%20changed%20and%20even%20the%20connotations%20of%20words.%20But%20some%20things%20have%20remained%20intact%20like%20the%20strong%20shoulders%20of%20palanquin%20bearers%2C%20or%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekahars%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Carrying%20Brahmins%2C%20priests%2C%20kings%2C%20and%20other%20landlords%20in%20palanquins%20and%20ferrying%20them%20to%20their%20destinations%20was%20their%20job.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20261px)%2085vw%2C%20261px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-715x1024.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22261%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-715x1024.jpg%20715w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742-210x300.jpg%20210w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30093107%2FIMG_2742.jpg%20838w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22374%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20was%20a%20time%20when%20K%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eahars%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20did%20not%20even%20have%20slippers%20on%20their%20feet.%20When%20they%20moved%20with%20the%20heavy%20load%20on%20their%20shoulders%2C%20they%20used%20to%20make%20a%20unique%20sound%20to%20boost%20their%20spirits.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20one%20finds%20mention%20of%20slavery%20in%20the%20history%20of%20western%20countries%2C%20the%20concept%20has%20been%20concealed%20behind%20the%20veil%20of%20caste%20in%20Indian%20history.%20Kahar%20and%20Kamkar%20were%20caste%20groups%20whose%20members%20were%20forced%20to%20bear%20the%20burden%20of%20others.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20present%2C%20the%20Kahars%2C%20or%20Chandravanshis%20of%20the%20feudal%20system%2C%20primarily%20reside%20in%20Bengal%2C%20Bihar%20and%20the%20eastern%20areas%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20in%20addition%20to%20other%20states.%20They%20did%20not%20have%20any%20rights%20on%20agricultural%20land%20or%20farming%2C%20nor%20do%20they%20have%20many%20rights%20now.%20Today%2C%20they%20are%20only%20sought%20after%20when%20someone%20is%20getting%20married.%20They%20used%20to%20work%20as%20a%20group%20and%20chose%20the%20palanquin%20or%20the%20group%20as%20per%20their%20status.%20Generally%2C%20they%20worked%20in%20groups%20of%20four%20%E2%80%93%20two%20each%20at%20the%20front%20and%20the%20back%20%E2%80%93%20while%20the%20person%20sitting%20in%20the%20palanquin%20at%20the%20centre%20travelled%20comfortably.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20their%20sincerity%20in%20the%20job%2C%20the%20members%20of%20this%20caste%20group%20have%20been%20oppressed%20a%20lot%20in%20the%20feudal%20system.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20times%20have%20changed%20and%20science%20and%20technology%20have%20advanced.%20Roads%20have%20been%20built.%20Uneven%20and%20narrow%20walkways%20are%20gone%20and%20vehicles%20have%20become%20available.%20Yet%20even%20now%2C%20affluent%20people%20seek%20their%20services%20while%20planning%20a%20wedding.%20The%20number%20of%20palanquin-bearers%20has%20reduced%20significantly%20now.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20crisis%20of%20livelihood%20is%20looming%20over%20the%20community.%20They%20already%20had%20a%20dearth%20of%20land%20and%20whatever%20little%20bit%20of%20land%20there%20was%2C%20has%20been%20divided%20further.%20It%20is%20difficult%20to%20say%20how%20much%20immovable%20property%20is%20owned%20by%20the%20present%20generation%20of%20this%20caste%20group.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20documents%20of%20Bihar%20government%2C%20their%20total%20population%20is%202%2C155%2C644%20and%20they%20are%20included%20in%20the%20extremely%20backward%20class.%20Though%20they%20are%20not%20considered%20%E2%80%98untouchable%E2%80%99%2C%20their%20condition%20is%20no%20better%20than%20that%20of%20Dalit%20communities%E2%80%99.%20For%20example%2C%20only%201.5%25%20to%202%25%20of%20their%20population%20participates%20in%20government%20jobs%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20caste%20group%20is%20in%20the%20grip%20of%20political%20Hinduisation%20now.%20To%20alienate%20them%20from%20the%20OBC%20community%2C%20they%20are%20being%20told%20that%20they%20are%20not%20Kahar%20but%20Chandravanshi.%20For%20example%2C%20it%20is%20claimed%20that%20the%20Chandravansh%2C%20or%20lunar%20dynasty%2C%20was%20a%20Kshatriya%20caste%20of%20ancient%20India.%20Sometimes%2C%20to%20pit%20them%20against%20the%20Yadavas%2C%20it%20is%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Hindu%20deity%20Krishna%20was%20born%20in%20the%20Yaduvansh%20branch%20of%20the%20Chandravansh.%20They%20even%20call%20Kahar%20caste%20members%20descendants%20of%20Jarasandha.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChange%20is%20necessary%20because%20other%20OBC%20caste%20groups%20often%20do%20not%20mingle%20with%20them%20while%20Dalits%20do%20not%20consider%20them%20one%20of%20their%20own.%20One%20needs%20to%20understand%20the%20social%2C%20political%20and%20economic%20dilemma%20of%20this%20caste.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Hindi%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%20Read%20the%20Hindi%20original%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F263539%2Fbihar-caste-survey-kahaar-caste-society%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20earlier%20parts%20of%20the%20series%20on%20the%20following%20communities%20by%20clicking%20on%20their%20names%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-caste-survey-the-whos-who-in-the-data-ghasi%5C%22%3EGhasi%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbihar-cast