imesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussian-court-jails-veteran-activist-orlov-for-2-5-years%2Famp_articleshow%2F108045617.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussian-court-jails-veteran-activist-orlov-for-2-5-years%2Famp_articleshow%2F108045617.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Quietly%20Renaming%20'Passenger%20Trains'%20and%20Raising%20Fares%2C%20Railways%20Restore%20Pre-COVID%20Rates%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F27163018%2F21323848_8c73135d33_e.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Indian%20Railways%20on%20February%2027%20restored%20the%20Second%20Class%20Ordinary%20Fares%20on%20%E2%80%98Passenger%20Trains%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20had%20been%20renamed%20as%20%E2%80%98Express%20Specials%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98MEMU%2FDEMU%20Express%E2%80%99%20Trains%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftamil-nadu%2Frailways-restore-passenger-train-fares%2Farticle67890663.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereports%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20lockdown%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20the%20Railways%20had%20been%20criticised%20for%20their%20gradual%20withdrawal%20of%20%E2%80%98Passenger%20Trains%E2%80%99%20by%20simply%20changing%20their%20names.%20%E2%80%98Ordinary%20Class%E2%80%99%20fares%20were%20done%20away%20with%20and%20the%20minimum%20cost%20of%20ticket%20went%20up%20from%20Rs%2010%20to%20a%20whopping%20three-fold%2C%20to%20Rs%2030.%20This%20was%20at%20par%20with%20Express%20Train%20fares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20railway%20sources%2C%20writes%20the%20newspaper%2C%20the%20Chief%20Booking%20Reservation%20Supervisors%20were%20informed%20that%20the%20minimum%20fare%20in%20Second%20Class%20Ordinary%20Trains%20had%20been%20reversed%20with%20effect%20from%20the%20early%20hours.%20It%20is%20believed%20that%20this%20followed%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20Railway%20Board%20on%20February%2026%20to%20take%20a%20decision%20on%20the%20slashing%20of%20fares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20Railways%20had%20come%20under%20criticism%20for%20charging%20commuters%2C%20%E2%80%9Cespecially%20small%20vendors%2C%20daily%20wage%20workers%20and%20other%20poor%20passengers%2C%20are%20paying%20double%20the%20charge%20for%20travelling%20in%20the%20same%20slow-moving%20train.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReports%20recorded%20how%20the%20change%20in%20name%2C%20without%20a%20change%20in%20speed%20had%20resulted%20in%20higher%20prices%20paid%20by%20those%20who%20could%20least%20afford%20to.%20The%20move%20will%20bolster%20the%20Railways%20financially%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Fexplainers%2Fhas-indian-railways-replaced-passenger-trains-with-express-specials-what-will-be-the-fare-structure-8793114.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%20a%20news%20report%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20yesterday%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20it%20will%20be%20a%20huge%20burden%20to%20the%20economically%20disadvantaged%20commuters%20such%20as%20small%20vendors%2C%20daily%20wage%20labourers%2C%20farmers%20who%20depend%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Caffordable%E2%80%9D%20fares%20of%20the%20trains%20for%20transportation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20role%20of%20the%20Indian%20railways%20as%20a%20public%20good%2C%20to%20enable%20the%20least%20advantaged%20in%20a%20large%20country%20was%20questioned%20by%20others.%20Former%20railway%20officer%2C%20Mathew%20John%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-indian-railways-hype-and-reality%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewrote%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20Indian%20Railways%20%