ave%20been%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Frafah-gaza-palestinians-displaced-tents%2F%5C%22%3Eforced%20to%20flee%3C%2Fa%3E.%20More%20than%20an%20open%20secret%2C%20the%20phenomenon%20has%20been%20widely%20%E2%80%94%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Fisraeli-journalists-pr-army-october-7%2F%5C%22%3Euncritically%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%94%20reported%20in%20the%20Israeli%20media%2C%20while%20rabbis%20from%20the%20Religious%20Zionist%20movement%20have%20been%20answering%20soldiers%E2%80%99%20questions%20about%20what%20is%20permissible%20to%20loot%20according%20to%20Jewish%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoldiers%20who%20returned%20from%20fighting%20in%20Gaza%20confirmed%20to%20%2B972%20Magazine%20and%20Local%20Call%20that%20the%20phenomenon%20is%20ubiquitous%2C%20and%20that%20for%20the%20most%20part%20their%20commanders%20are%20allowing%20it%20to%20happen.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20took%20things%20%E2%80%94%20mugs%2C%20books%2C%20each%20one%20the%20souvenir%20that%20does%20it%20for%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20one%20soldier%2C%20who%20admitted%20that%20he%20himself%20took%20a%20%E2%80%9Csouvenir%E2%80%9D%20from%20one%20of%20the%20medical%20centers%20that%20the%20army%20occupied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20soldier%2C%20who%20served%20in%20northern%20and%20central%20Gaza%2C%20testified%20that%20soldiers%20%E2%80%9Ctook%20rugs%2C%20blankets%2C%20%5Band%5D%20kitchen%20utensils%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20explained%20that%20there%20was%20no%20briefing%20on%20the%20matter%20from%20the%20army%20either%20before%20entering%20or%20while%20in%20the%20field.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20zero%20talk%20about%20it%20from%20the%20commanders%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CEveryone%20knows%20that%20people%20are%20taking%20things.%20It%E2%80%99s%20considered%20funny%20%E2%80%94%20people%20say%3A%20%E2%80%98Send%20me%20to%20The%20Hague.%E2%80%99%20It%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20happen%20in%20secret.%20The%20commanders%20saw%2C%20everyone%20knows%2C%20and%20no%20one%20seems%20to%20care.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20soldier%20offered%20his%20explanation%20for%20why%20the%20phenomenon%20is%20so%20widespread%3A%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20something%20about%20this%20reality%20in%20which%20the%20house%20is%20already%20%5Bin%20ruins%5D%20that%20allows%20you%20to%20take%20a%20plate%20or%20rug.%20In%20one%20of%20the%20operations%2C%20in%20a%20destroyed%20house%2C%20there%20was%20a%20cupboard%20with%20antique%20kitchen%20utensils%2C%20special%20plates%2C%20special%20mugs.%20I%20saw%20them%20being%20looted%2C%20unfortunately.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%5BThe%20commanders%5D%20didn%E2%80%99t%20really%20talk%20to%20us%20about%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20another%20soldier%20testified.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20didn%E2%80%99t%20say%20you%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20take%20things.%20And%20most%20people%20felt%20the%20need%20to%20take%20a%20souvenir.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20soldier%20noted%20that%20the%20looting%20was%20no%20secret%3B%20indeed%2C%20some%20of%20their%20seniors%20were%20doing%20it%20too.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20company%20sergeant%20major%20distributed%20Qur%E2%80%99an%20study%20books%20that%20he%20found%20and%20gave%20to%20whomever%20wanted%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CAnother%20soldier%20took%20a%20set%20of%20coffee%20mugs%2C%20a%20serving%20tray%2C%20and%20a%20pot.%20Another%20unit%2C%20whom%20we%20met%20after%20they%20returned%20from%20a%20tour%2C%20brought%20a%20motorcycle%2C%20like%20the%20Nukhba%20%5BHamas%20special%20forces%5D%20motorcycles.%20One%20of%20the%20soldiers%20declared%20that%20it%20was%20his.%20They%20%5Bthe%20soldiers%5D%20talked%20about%20renovating%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20soldier%20who%20served%20in%20Gaza%20told%20%2B972%20and%20Local%20Call%20that%20soldiers%20took%20%E2%80%9Cprayer%20beads%2C%20spoons%2C%20glasses%2C%20coffee%20pots%2C%20jewelry%2C%20rings.%20Whatever%20is%20easy%20and%20accessible%20is%20taken.%20Not%20everything%2C%20but%20people%20felt%20like%20the%20lords%20of%20the%20land.%E2%80%9D%20He%20noted%20also%20that%20%E2%80%9Cmaps%20from%20children%E2%80%99s%20textbooks%20were%20taken%20to%20show%20how%20they%20are%20taught%20there.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%20to%20the%20others%20who%20testified%2C%20this%20soldier%20said%20that%20it%20was%20clear%20to%20him%20that%20looting%20was%20forbidden.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20experience%2C%20of%20course%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20big%20no%20no%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explained.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20emphasised%20this%20issue%2C%20but%20no%20one%20supervises%20the%20reservists.%20The%20most%20common%20thing%20%5Bto%20steal%5D%20is%20%E2%80%98local%20souvenirs%E2%80%99%20%5Bi.e.%20quintessentially%20Palestinian%20or%20Arab%20items%5D.%20Once%2C%20they%20kicked%20out%20a%20soldier%20who%20stole%20money.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Findias-water-transport-workers-union-says-wont-help-ships-carrying-arms-bound-for-israel%5C%22%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20Water%20Transport%20Workers%E2%80%99%20Union%20Says%20Won%E2%80%99t%20Help%20Ships%20Carrying%20Arms%20Bound%20for%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20soldier%20added%20that%20he%20and%20his%20team%20tried%2C%20with%20varying%20degrees%20of%20success%2C%20to%20persuade%20other%20soldiers%20to%20leave%20behind%20the%20items%20they%20had%20stolen%20in%20Gaza.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20%5Bsoldiers%5D%20would%20come%20back%20with%20things%3B%20we%20told%20them%20it%20was%20better%20to%20leave%20them%20%5Binside%20the%20Strip%2C%20near%20the%20fence%5D%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20better%20to%20throw%20them%20away%20than%20to%20take%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98From%20the%20ruins%20of%20Khan%20Younis%2C%20in%20the%20classic%20Gazan%20style%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ynet.co.il%2Fblogs%2F137daysofwar%2Farticle%2Fsysxyvzz2t%5C%22%3Ecommunique%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0this%20week%20to%20commanders%20in%20charge%20of%20units%20fighting%20in%20Gaza%2C%20IDF%20Chief%20of%20Staff%20Herzi%20Halevi%20urged%20soldiers%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20to%20take%20anything%20that%20is%20not%20ours.%E2%80%9D%20But%20this%20letter%20comes%20after%20several%20months%20in%20which%20looting%20has%20become%20completely%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20normalised%20is%20the%20phenomenon%20that%20in%20a%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMistaclim%2Fstatus%2F1756570168493248640%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Esegment%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20public%20broadcaster%2C%20Kan%2C%20soldiers%20presented%20reporter%20Uri%20Levy%20with%20a%20mirror%20they%20had%20brought%20back%20from%20Gaza.%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20the%20ruins%20of%20Khan%20Younis%2C%20in%20the%20classic%20Gazan%20style%2C%E2%80%9D%20Levy%20jokes%2C%20without%20asking%20the%20soldiers%20where%20they%20found%20the%20mirror%20or%20why%20they%20stole%20it.%20In%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ynet.co.il%2Fyedioth%2Farticle%2Fb16pe00zot%5C%22%3Ecolumn%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20Ynet%2C%20Nahum%20Barnea%20quotes%20a%20soldier%20who%20said%20he%20saw%20the%20looting%20of%20%E2%80%9Cphones%2C%20vacuum%20cleaners%2C%20motorcycles%2C%20and%20bicycles.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChannel%2013%20also%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D1800211080447254%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20the%20phenomenon%20earlier%20this%20month.%20Rather%20than%20condemning%20it%2C%20however%2C%20the%20presenters%20simply%20noted%20that%20the%20videos%20are%20being%20shared%20around%20the%20world%20to%20%E2%80%9Cshame%E2%80%9D%20Israeli%20soldiers.%20(The%20segment%20also%20included%20an%20interview%20with%20the%20soldier%20who%20filmed%20himself%20with%20the%20wristwatches%20he%20found%20inside%20a%20Palestinian%20home%2C%20who%20claims%20that%20he%20did%20not%20steal%20them%3A%20%E2%80%9CThey%20see%20me%20holding%20watches%2C%20not%20looting%2C%20nothing%20%E2%80%A6%20My%20intention%20was%20to%20show%20that%20the%20Hamas%20leadership%20lives%20there%20at%20a%20high%20level.%E2%80%9D)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20sign%20of%20how%20widespread%20the%20phenomenon%20has%20become%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20rabbis%20from%20the%20Religious%20Zionist%20movement%20have%20been%20receiving%20questions%20from%20soldiers%20on%20the%20issue.%20In%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DieosKCEiHvg%5C%22%3EQ%26amp%3BA%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0uploaded%20to%20YouTube%2C%20Rabbi%20Yitzchak%20Sheilat%20of%20the%20Ma%E2%80%99ale%20Adumim%20Yeshiva%20in%20the%20occupied%20West%20Bank%20noted%20that%20looting%20is%20forbidden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20very%20serious%20issue%2C%20in%20two%20respects%3A%20in%20terms%20of%20halacha%20%5BJewish%20law%5D%20and%20military%20law%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CHalacha%20permits%20looting%20only%20food%20or%20perishable%20things%20from%20the%20enemy%20%E2%80%A6%20taking%20objects%20is%20strictly%20prohibited.%20According%20to%20halacha%2C%20all%20the%20spoils%20must%20go%20to%20the%20king%2C%20that%20is%2C%20the%20army%20commander%20%E2%80%A6%20It%20would%20be%20a%20shame%20for%20someone%20to%20be%20caught%20and%20have%20to%20pay%20a%20heavy%20price.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20soldiers%20asked%20the%20rabbi%20if%20it%20is%20permissible%20to%20take%20things%20from%20a%20house%20before%20it%20is%20demolished.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20forbidden%20to%20take%20things%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sheilat%20answered.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20take%20something%2C%20it%20must%20be%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20chief%20of%20staff.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20if%20a%20commander%20approves%20taking%20things%20for%20the%20company%3F%E2%80%9D%20a%20soldier%20asked.%20%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20exactly%20the%20problem%2C%20that%20there%20are%20commanders%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20military%20law%2C%20or%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20know%2C%20and%20suddenly%20they%20allow%20guys%20%5Bto%20do%5D%20things%20they%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20allow%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sheilat%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Rabbi%20Shmuel%20Eliyahu%2C%20the%20chief%20rabbi%20of%20the%20northern%20city%20of%20Safed%2C%20offered%20a%20different%20perspective%20on%20the%20issue%20in%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yeshiva.org.il%2Fmidrash%2F52638%5C%22%3EQ%26amp%3BA%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0of%20his%20own.%20He%20explained%20that%20because%20the%20%E2%80%9CArabs%20in%20Gaza%20do%20not%20observe%20international%20conventions%2C%20we%20are%20not%20obliged%20to%20abide%20by%20any%20of%20the%20rules%20of%20war.%20Nonetheless%2C%20we%20are%20very%20careful%2C%20because%20we%20want%20to%20preserve%20the%20image%20of%20God%20within%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20should%20be%20noted%20that%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cindependent%E2%80%9D%20looting%20by%20soldiers%2C%20there%20is%20a%20special%20unit%20in%20the%20Israeli%20army%20dedicated%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.walla.co.il%2Fitem%2F3625176%5C%22%3Eseizing%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0money%20and%20other%20property%20found%20in%20the%20battlefield.%20So%20far%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.israelhayom.co.il%2Fnews%2Fdefense%2Farticle%2F15226630%5C%22%3Eit%20is%20known%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20the%20military%20has%20seized%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20shekels%20from%20Gaza%2C%20which%20it%20claims%20belonged%20to%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98And%20you%20shall%20eat%20the%20riches%20of%20all%20the%20nations%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlongside%20the%20looting%20of%20Palestinians%E2%80%99%20belongings%2C%20Israeli%20soldiers%20are%20also%20routinely%20eating%20the%20food%20they%20find%20in%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20abandoned%20homes.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20two%20or%20three%20weeks%2C%20soldiers%20use%20whatever%20they%20find%2C%20clean%20it%2C%20and%20disinfect%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20soldier%20told%20%2B972%20and%20Local%20Call%20%E2%80%94%20though%2C%20according%20to%20him%2C%20soldiers%20are%20not%20supposed%20to%20use%20food%20found%20in%20Palestinian%20homes%20in%20case%20it%20is%20contaminated.%20Others%20said%20that%20no%20precise%20instructions%20were%20given%20regarding%20how%20to%20behave%20while%20staying%20in%20houses%2C%20many%20of%20which%20are%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com%2Fisrael-news%2F2024-01-31%2Fty-article%2F.premium%2Fisraeli-army-occupies-gaza-homes-then-burns-them-down%2F0000018d-6021-d16e-a39f-7f3f01e30000%5C%22%3Eset%20on%20fire%20or%20blown%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0by%20the%20army%20once%20they%20are%20no%20longer%20of%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.co.il%2Ffood%2F2024-02-13%2Fty-article-magazine%2F.premium%2F0000018d-82c5-d6dc-ab9f-cffd1ebc0000%5C%22%3Erecent%20Haaretz%20article%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Israeli%20soldiers%20described%20their%20%E2%80%9Cexperiences%E2%80%9D%20of%20cooking%20in%20Palestinian%20homes%20using%20the%20ingredients%20they%20found%20there.%20%E2%80%9CGazan%20cuisine%2C%20from%20what%20we%E2%80%99ve%20seen%2C%20is%20full%20of%20spices%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%20soldier%20said%20in%20the%20article.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20every%20house%20you%E2%80%99ll%20find%20a%20lot%20of%20ras%20el%20hanout%20style%20mixes.%20There%20are%20also%20plenty%20of%20lentils%2C%20so%20at%20first%20we%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20stews%20%E2%80%A6.%20Every%20house%20we%20stayed%20in%20had%20olives%20that%20%5BPalestinians%5D%20make%2C%20which%20we%20tasted%20%E2%80%A6%20Olive%20oil%20is%20also%20present%20in%20every%20home%2C%20in%20gallons%2C%20and%20it%20helps%20a%20lot%20to%20upgrade%20any%20food.%20They%20also%20have%20a%20great%20spicy%20sauce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSometimes%20you%20encounter%20special%20things%20%E2%80%94%20suddenly%20there%E2%80%99s%20garlic%20and%20then%20you%20go%20all%20out%20on%20pasta%20with%20tomatoes%20and%20garlic%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20soldier%20continued.%20%E2%80%9CI%20also%20came%20across%20this%20carob%20sauce%20that%20we%20added%20to%20the%20porridge%20and%20it%20was%20excellent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fjobs-in-israel-labour-activists-trade-unions-raise-concerns-over-no-protections-for-indian-workers%5C%22%3EJobs%20in%20Israel%3A%20Labour%20Activists%2C%20Trade%20Unions%20Raise%20Concerns%20Over%20No%20Protections%20for%20Indian%20Workers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.srugim.co.il%2F883163-%25D7%259E%25D7%25A6%25D7%2590%25D7%25A0%25D7%2595-%25D7%2590%25D7%2595%25D7%259B%25D7%259C-%25D7%2591%25D7%259C%25D7%2599-%25D7%259B%25D7%25A9%25D7%25A8%25D7%2595%25D7%25AA-%25D7%2591%25D7%2591%25D7%2599%25D7%25AA-%25D7%2591%25D7%25A2%25D7%2596%25D7%2594-%25D7%2594%25D7%2590%25D7%259D-%25D7%259E%25D7%2595%25D7%25AA%25D7%25A8%23google_vignette%5C%22%3Eletter%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0published%20by%20the%20military%20rabbinate%20detailed%20instructions%20on%20how%20to%20keep%20kosher%20when%20using%20food%20and%20utensils%20found%20in%20homes%20in%20Gaza.%20The%20letter%2C%20signed%20by%20Rabbi%20Avishai%20Peretz%20ends%20with%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chabad.org%2Flibrary%2Fbible_cdo%2Faid%2F15992%2Fjewish%2FChapter-61.htm%5C%22%3Ebiblical%20directive%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20you%20shall%20eat%20the%20riches%20of%20all%20the%20nations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERabbi%20Sheilat%20also%20addressed%20the%20issue%20of%20whether%20it%20is%20permissible%20to%20eat%20food%20found%20in%20Palestinian%20homes%20in%20his%20Q%26amp%3BA.%20%E2%80%9CWith%20regard%20to%20non-kosher%20foods%2C%20there%20is%20a%20difference%20between%20what%20happens%20when%20you%20find%20food%20in%20enemy%20homes%2C%20where%20the%20law%20is%20that%20if%20you%20find%20food%20that%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%2C%20and%20you%20want%20that%20food%2C%20even%20if%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20essential%2C%20say%20sweets%20%E2%80%A6%20it%E2%80%99s%20permitted%20to%20eat%20them%20without%20worrying%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20kosher%20or%20not.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20%2B972%20and%20Local%20Call%2C%20the%20IDF%20Spokesperson%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20IDF%20views%20with%20severity%20any%20case%20in%20which%20soldiers%20act%20contrary%20to%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20IDF%2C%20including%20cases%20of%20unlawful%20taking%20of%20property.%20IDF%20commanders%20in%20various%20units%20conduct%20an%20ongoing%20dialogue%20on%20the%20subject%20throughout%20the%20fighting.%20Every%20report%20received%20on%20the%20subject%20is%20examined%20and%20dealt%20with%20individually.%20In%20relevant%20cases%2C%20an%20investigation%20is%20opened%20by%20the%20military%20police%2C%20and%20in%20some%20cases%20suspects%20are%20detained%20for%20interrogation%20purposes.%20The%20IDF%20operates%20in%20accordance%20with%20international%20law%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20do%20so.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EThis%20article%20first%20appeared%20on%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0%2B972%20Magazine%3Ci%3E.%20Read%20it%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Fisraeli-soldiers-looting-gaza%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3EA%20version%20of%20this%20article%20was%20first%20published%20in%20Hebrew%20on%20Local%20Call.%20Read%20it%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mekomit.co.il%2F%25d7%259b%25d7%2595%25d7%259c%25d7%259d-%25d7%259c%25d7%2595%25d7%25a7%25d7%2597%25d7%2599%25d7%259d-%25d7%2594%25d7%259e%25d7%25a4%25d7%25a7%25d7%2593%25d7%2599%25d7%259d-%25d7%2599%25d7%2595%25d7%2593%25d7%25a2%25d7%2599%25d7%259d-%25d7%2597%25d7%2599%25d7%2599%25d7%259c%25d7%2599%25d7%259d-%25d7%259e%25d7%25a2%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3Ehere%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709031633000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22htt