0for%20asking%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3Eone%20day%20suddenly%20some%20day%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3Etaking%20a%20deep%20breath%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EShe%20will%20turn%20her%20face%20away%20quietly.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20the%20lines%20from%20late%20poet%20Raghuvir%20Sahay%E2%80%99s%20poem%20%E2%80%98Uska%20Man%E2%80%99.%20In%20the%20poem%2C%20he%20is%20talking%20about%20a%20woman.%20But%2C%20as%20is%20the%20case%20with%20every%20great%20poem%2C%20its%20pronoun%20can%20be%20used%20in%20different%20contexts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20context%20of%20today%E2%80%99s%20India%2C%20does%20this%20pronoun%20%E2%80%98she%E2%80%99%20represent%20the%20collective%20noun%20we%20know%20as%20public%3F%20Not%20getting%20information%20can%20be%20a%20reason%20for%20being%20distraught.%20Just%20as%20it%20is%20difficult%20for%20a%20woman%20to%20survive%20as%20an%20individual%20without%20information%2C%20information%20is%20the%20lifeline%20for%20people%20in%20any%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20poem%20came%20to%20my%20mind%20when%20I%20saw%20YouTuber%20Dhruv%20Rathee%E2%80%99s%20latest%20video%20that%20is%20creating%20a%20sensation%20on%20social%20media%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20thought%2C%20and%20not%20wrongly%2C%20that%20India%20was%20sleepwalking%20into%20a%20dictatorship%2C%20the%20news%20of%20this%20video%20being%20watched%20by%20more%20than%2010%20million%20people%20came%20as%20a%20shock%20to%20many%20of%20us.%20Especially%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20video%20is%20getting%20popular%20among%20the%20youth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FY9253_M38Xk%3Fsi%3DLsSg73AwSQQ0F-sk%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20big%20media%20platforms%20have%20deployed%20all%20their%20resources%20to%20glorify%20this%20government%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20when%20the%20same%20name%20is%20being%20chanted%20everywhere%2C%20when%20all%20that%20our%20top%20intellectuals%20say%20is%20that%20in%20May%202024%2C%20Modi%20will%20return%20as%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20when%20we%20are%20told%20that%20the%20die%20is%20cast%2C%20just%20then%20a%20video%20appears%20warning%20the%20people%20that%20they%20are%20offering%20themselves%20to%20a%20dictator%20and%20starts%20spreading%20like%20fire.%20What%20does%20it%20mean%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20this%20a%20sign%20that%20there%20is%20still%20a%20hunger%20to%20know%20the%20truth%20in%20India%3F%20Are%20the%20people%20of%20India%20ready%20to%20fight%20to%20save%20themselves%20from%20being%20transformed%20from%20citizens%20into%20subjects%3F%20At%20a%20time%20when%20almost%20everyone%20has%20given%20up%20because%20no%20one%20wants%20to%20hear%20anything%2C%20what%20does%20the%20extraordinary%20viewership%20of%20this%20video%20tell%20us%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20Dhruv%20explains%2C%20very%20calmly%2C%20why%20and%20how%20dictatorship%20is%20gradually%20taking%20root%20in%20India%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20democracy.%20The%20point%20is%20being%20made%20in%20a%20logical%20manner%20and%20without%20any%20excitement%20or%20pompous%20words.%20Perhaps%20this%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20this%20video%20is%20being%20watched.%20Dhruv%20is%20not%20saying%20anything%20new%2C%20this%20analysis%20has%20been%20reported%20many%20times%20and%20by%20many%20people%20before%20him.%20But%20it%20should%20not%20undermine%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESupporters%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20fear%20that%20the%20viewers%20of%20this%20video%20might%20primarily%20belong%20to%20the%20age%20group%20of%20first%20and%20second%20time%20voters.%20This%20is%20not%20an%20unfounded%20fear.%20I%20heard%20my%20wife%E2%80%99s%20nephew%20calling%20from%20Mumbai%20asking%20her%20to%20watch%20this%20video.%20He%20is%20not%20a%20typical%20Modi%20detractor.%20There%20would%20be%20many%20like%20him%20asking%20their%20parents%20and%20relatives%20to%20watch%20it.%20That%20is%20alarming%20for%20the%20Bhartiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20and%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20proof%20of%20the%20video%E2%80%99s%20impact%20is%20that%20the%20pro-government%20camp%20has%20already%20pressed%20some%20social%20media%20influencers%20into%20action%20to%20counter%20Rathee.%20All%20of%20a%20sudden%20there%20are%20also%20those%20recalling%20Rathee%E2%80%99s%20political%20inclination%2C%20informing%20us%20that%20he%20has%20been%20a%20supporter%20of%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%2C%20hence%20there%20must%20be%20an%20ulterior%20motive%20behind%20this%20video.%20There%20is%20also%20an%20argument%20that%20while%20Rathee%20is%20calling%20Modi%20a%20dictator%20in%20the%20video%2C%20signs%20of%20dictatorship%20can%20be%20found%20in%20the%20politics%20of%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoes%20this%20prove%20the%20point%20of%20this%20video%20wrong%3F%20Do%20the%20facts%20and%20arguments%20of%20this%20video%20become%20false%20because%20Rathee%E2%80%99s%20political%20sympathies%20lie%20with%20a%20party%20which%20can%20be%20potentially%20dangerous%3F%20Should%20Rathee%20have%20also%20told%20his%20viewers%20that%20there%20is%20a%20danger%20of%20Kejriwal%20becoming%20a%20dictator%20and%20only%20then%20his%20analysis%20of%20Modi%20would%20become%20credible%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20we%20saying%20that%20it%20is%20pointless%20to%20criticise%20the%20BJP%20or%20Modi%20because%20others%20can%20also%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20the%20same%3F%20If%20we%20are%20looking%20for%20a%20pure%20democratic%20leader%20and%20party%20upon%20whose%20arrival%20only%20should%20this%20government%20be%20replaced%2C%20then%20we%20are%20preparing%20to%20push%20ourselves%20into%20an%20abyss%20that%20we%20will%20never%20escape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERathee%20is%20giving%20information%20which%20is%20the%20lifeblood%20of%20democracy.%20It%20is%20not%20surprising%20that%20the%20first%20thing%20a%20dictator%20wants%20to%20do%20is%20to%20clamp%20down%20on%20sources%20of%20information.%20There%20will%20be%20only%20one%20source%20of%20information%20and%20that%20is%20the%20mouth%20of%20the%20dictator.%20The%20rest%20will%20only%20be%20his%20loudspeakers.%20Be%20it%20Stalin%20or%20Mao%2C%20Hitler%20or%20Mussolini%2C%20every%20dictator%20wants%20this.%20Just%20his%20image%2C%20just%20his%20voice.%20The%20leader%20is%20the%20journalist%2C%20the%20economist%2C%20the%20sociologist%2C%20the%20poet%2C%20the%20psychologist%20and%20the%20philosopher.%20He%20is%20the%20chief%20priest%20and%20he%20is%20the%20king.%20When%20one%20voice%20continues%20to%20be%20poured%20day%20and%20night%20in%20the%20public%E2%80%99s%20ears%2C%20they%20gradually%20lose%20the%20ability%20to%20listen%20to%20other%20voices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20such%20a%20time%2C%20those%20who%20understand%20the%20value%20of%20democracy%20fulfil%20their%20duty%20of%20keeping%20the%20public%E2%80%99s%20ears%20alive%2C%20regardless%20of%20how%20many%20ears%20are%20ready%20for%20it.%20Their%20job%20is%20to%20keep%20the%20ears%20alert.%20And%20for%20that%2C%20the%20nutrition%20of%20true%20information%20is%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20popularity%20of%20Rathee%E2%80%99s%20video%20only%20means%20that%20this%20is%20no%20time%20to%20become%20pessimistic%20before%20the%20inevitability%20of%20dictatorship.%20People%20want%20to%20live.%20And%20what%20should%20we%20do%20if%20we%20love%20these%20people%20who%20want%20to%20live%3F%20Act%20like%20Dhruv%20Rathee.%20It%20is%20not%20very%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EApoorvanand%20is%20an%20academic%20and%20an%20author.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709029761000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2F28140827%2FIMG_0205.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fresisting-dictatorship-one-video-at-a-time%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20a%20time%20when%20big%20media%20platforms%20have%20deployed%20all%20their%20resources%20to%20glorify%20the%20government%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20a%20video%20asking%20if%20India%20is%20headed%20towards%20dictatorship%20getting%20mass%20viewership%20assumes%20greater%20significance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A36%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fresisting-dictatorship-one-video-at-a-time%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%3A%20Cops%20Rescue%20Woman%20Hounded%20for%20'Blasphemy'%20Over%20Dress%20With%20Arabic%20Calligraphy%20Prints%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fblasphemy-carousel.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20woman%20in%20Ichra%20Bazaar%20in%20Lahore%2C%20Pakistan%20was%20hounded%20by%20a%20mob%20on%20Sunday%2C%20February%2025%2C%20alleging%20she%20had%20committed%20blasphemy%20since%20she%20was%20wearing%20a%20dress%20with%20Arabic%20calligraphy.%20Eventually%2C%20the%20local%20police%20managed%20to%20rescue%20and%20take%20her%20from%20the%20crowded%20area%2C%20as%20per%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1817307%2Fsituation-unfolded-due-to-confusion-says-lahore-cop-after-rescuing-woman-in-arabic-print-shirt-from-mob%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDawn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20report%2C%20the%20episode%20occurred%20when%20the%20woman%20visited%20a%20shop%20with%20her%20husband%20and%20a%20man%20from%20the%20locality%20asked%20her%20to%20change%20her%20clothes%20and%20other%20people%20joined%20him%20%E2%80%9Cconsidering%20it%20a%20religious%20matter%E2%80%9D%20and%20charged%20the%20women%20for%20wearing%20a%20shirt%20which%20they%20assumed%20had%20%E2%80%9CQuranic%20verses%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20some%20shopkeepers%20defended%20the%20woman%20and%20sheltered%20her%20in%20a%20shop%20and%20even%20tried%20clarifying%20to%20the%20mob%20that%20the%20word%20in%20her%20dress%20was%20just%20an%20Arabic%20calligraphy%20print.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%201%3A30%20pm%2C%20we%20received%20a%20call%20that%20a%20blasphemous%20act%20took%20place%20near%20Pakistan%20Chowk%20in%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20Ichra%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gulberg%20Circle%20ASP%20Shehr%20Bano%20was%20quoted%20by%20%3Cem%3EDawn.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20caller%20chose%20to%20stay%20anonymous%20and%20just%20mentioned%20that%20a%20woman%20was%20wearing%20a%20dress%20with%20calligraphy%20that%2C%20God%20forbid%2C%20seemed%20to%20be%20Quranic%20verses.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20viral%20video%20clip%2C%20the%20woman%20is%20seen%20shivering%20with%20fear%20and%20hiding%20in%20a%20shop%20as%20the%20mob%20surrounded%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-history-pakistan-blasphemy-law%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Wire%2527s%2520Zeeshan%2520Kaskar%2520spoke%2CZaheer%2520about%2520the%2520blasphemy%2520law.%26amp%3Btext%3DLast%2520week%252C%2520a%2520disturbing%2520video%2Cfire%2520to%2520his%2520dead%2520body.%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20the%20History%20of%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20Blasphemy%20Law%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20%3Cem%3EDawn%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%2C%20the%20police%20officers%20refuted%20the%20blasphemy%20allegations%20and%20underlined%20that%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EHalwa%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20written%20in%20Arabic%20calligraphy%20on%20the%20dress%20the%20girl%20was%20wearing%20was%20not%20a%20holy%20word.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20meaning%20of%20the%20word%20is%20literally%20sincerity%2C%20love%2C%20goodness%2C%20life%2C%20humanity%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bano%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20the%20ASP%20underlined%20that%20the%20police%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20transport%20the%20woman%20from%20the%20shop%20to%20the%20police%20vehicle%20since%20the%20area%20was%20crowded%20and%20congested%20which%20prevented%20them%20from%20taking%20their%20vehicle%20inside%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20police%20had%20to%20swiftly%20act%20as%20the%20shop%20opposite%20the%20one%20where%20the%20woman%20was%20supposedly%20being%20kept%20safe%20had%20a%20burning%20stove%20and%20the%20police%20feared%20the%20shop%20could%20be%20set%20ablaze%20if%20the%20people%20mobilised%2C%20as%20per%20the%20%3Cem%3EDawn%3C%2Fem%3E%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20time%2C%20our%20survival%20instinct%20kicked%20in%20that%20we%20need%20to%20get%20the%20woman%20out%20of%20here.%20We%20arranged%20a%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eburqa%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20covered%20her%20face%20and%20told%20people%20not%20to%20take%20the%20law%20into%20their%20hands%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bano%20was%20quoted%20by%20%3Cem%3EDawn%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20taking%20the%20woman%20away%20from%20the%20crowd%2C%20the%20police%20also%20informed%20the%20angry%20mob%20about%20the%20concept%20of%20verification%20in%20Islam%20and%20assured%20that%20prompt%20action%20would%20be%20taken%20if%20a%20blasphemous%20incident%20had%20taken%20place%2C%20as%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBano%20refused%20to%20reveal%20the%20woman%E2%80%99s%20identity%20to%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMob%20lynchings%20in%20Pakistan%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%202021%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uscirf.gov%2Fnews-room%2Fuscirf-spotlight%2Fenforcing-blasphemy-laws-have-dire-consequences%5C%22%3EUnited%20States%20Commission%20on%20International%20Religious%20Freedom%3C%2Fa%3E%20report%2C%20the%20instances%20of%20mob%20violence%20and%20criminal%20charges%20over%20religious%20issues%20are%20more%20common%20in%20Pakistan%20than%20anywhere%20e