20only%20targets%20cancer%20cells%20but%20also%20damages%20rapidly%20dividing%20healthy%20cells%2C%20including%20hair%20follicles.%20Studies%20indicate%20that%20approximately%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F37185388%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DChemotherapy%2520causes%2520substantial%2520thinning%2520or%2Cinterventional%2520options%2520have%2520been%2520limited.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E65%20percent%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20patients%20experience%20significant%20hair%20thinning%20or%20loss%20as%20a%20result%20of%20chemotherapy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20problem%20has%20been%20persistent%20since%20the%20advent%20of%20chemotherapy.%20There%20is%20an%20immense%20stigma%20attached%20to%20hair%20loss%20and%20cancer.%20If%20a%20woman%20goes%20bald%20suddenly%2C%20then%20people%20are%20quick%20to%20gossip%20about%20it.%20Besides%2C%20there%20are%20so%20many%20social%20or%20personal%20obligations%20where%20people%20wish%20to%20retain%20hair%20%E2%80%94%20from%20keeping%20the%20condition%20private%20from%20society%20to%20wanting%20a%20sense%20of%20normalcy%20for%20their%20family%20to%20name%20a%20few%2C%E2%80%9D%20Raghuveer%20Surupa%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20patient%20has%20an%20upcoming%20wedding%20or%20big%20event%2C%20then%20also%20they%20tend%20to%20delay%20their%20chemotherapies.%20It%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20people%20delay%20life-saving%20treatment%20for%20the%20fear%20of%20hair%20loss%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-1-1708521986.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Raghuveer%20designed%20a%20universal%20cap%20to%20protect%20hair%20follicles%20from%20chemotherapy